)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-change-careers-freelancing-side-hustle-earn-six-figures-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20tax%20expert%20shares%20the%20misconceptions%20and%20hidden%20costs%20the%20wealthy%20face%20when%20moving%20to%20Puerto%20Rico%20for%20tax%20breaks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20on%20a%20beach%20in%20Puerto%20Rico%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f99992895d822030322f98%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMany%20mainlanders%20are%20drawn%20to%20the%20beauty%20of%20Puerto%20Rico%20and%20the%20tax%20breaks.%3Cp%3EMaremagnum%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPuerto%20Rico's%20Act%2060%20offers%20tax%20incentives%20and%20is%20attracting%20wealthy%20Americans%20to%20the%20island.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHowever%2C%20there%20are%20misconceptions%20about%20what%20gains%20are%20exempt.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20of%20the%20important%20details%20often%20overlooked%20include%20residency%20and%20charitable%20contributions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretire-puerto-rico-tax-benefits-healthcare-residency-requirements-real-estate-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPuerto%20Rico%3C%2Fa%3E%20offers%20an%20enticing%20proposition%20for%20wealthy%20Americans%20from%20the%20mainland%20seeking%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpuerto-rico-act-60-tax-breaks-bona-fide-citizen-residency-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etax%20relief%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20making%20the%20move%20can%20be%20challenging%20if%20you%20are%20not%20familiar%20with%20all%20the%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.andersen.com%2Fpeople%2Fcole-clarissa%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EClarissa%20Cole%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20managing%20director%20at%20the%20tax%20advisor%20firm%20Anderson%20%E2%80%94%20which%20specializes%20in%20expatriation%20consequences%20and%20planning%2C%20especially%20for%20high%20net-worth%20individuals%20%E2%80%94%20said%20some%20of%20the%20important%20details%20often%20missed%20or%20overlooked%20include%20residency%2C%20investments%2C%20and%20charitable%20contributions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%202021%20and%202022%2C%20about%2027%2C000%20individuals%20moved%20from%20the%20US%20mainland%20to%20Puerto%20Rico%2C%20according%20to%20data%20collected%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.census.gov%2Ftopics%2Fpopulation%2Fmigration%2Fguidance%2Fstate-to-state-migration-flows.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20Census%20Bureau%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.investpr.org%2Fwhy-puerto-rico%2Ftax-benefits-policy%2F%3Fnis%3D6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EAct%2060%2C%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20provides%20financial%20incentives%20to%20entice%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretire-puerto-rico-tax-benefits-healthcare-residency-requirements-real-estate-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmericans%20to%20move%20to%20Puerto%20Rico%3C%2Fa%3E%20full-time%20for%20an%20extended%20period%2C%20has%20been%20a%20lure%20for%20some%20wealthy%20Americans%20seeking%20financial%20benefits%20without%20having%20to%20give%20up%20US%20citizenship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20qualify%20for%20an%20Act%2060%20decree%2C%20it%20includes%20a%204%25%20income%20tax%20rate%2C%20a%2075%25%20discount%20on%20property%20tax%2C%20and%20no%20tax%20on%20capital%20gains%20accrued%20while%20on%20the%20island.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20its%20core%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.investpr.org%2Fwhy-puerto-rico%2Ftax-benefits-policy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPuerto%20Rico's%20Act%2060%3C%2Fa%3E%20aims%20to%20invigorate%20its%20economy%20by%20attracting%20foreign%20residents%20and%20investors%2C%20especially%20those%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20money.%20However%2C%20to%20get%20the%20Act%2060%20benefits%2C%20you%20have%20to%20become%20what%20is%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpuerto-rico-act-60-tax-breaks-bona-fide-citizen-residency-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20%26quot%3Bbona%20fide%26quot%3B%20resident%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECommon%20misconceptions%20of%20the%20Puerto%20Rico%20tax%20breaks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECole%20said%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20misconceptions%20from%20people%20seeking%20tax%20breaks%20in%20Puerto%20Rico%20is%20that%20all%20gains%20from%20the%20selling%20of%20assets%2C%20such%20as%20a%20house%20or%20investments%2C%20are%20excluded%20once%20the%20person%20becomes%20a%20bona%20fide%20resident%20of%20the%20island.%20However%2C%20the%20true%20tax%20break%20is%20determined%20by%20how%20much%20of%20the%20gains%20came%20after%20becoming%20a%20resident%2C%20and%20this%20is%20determined%20by%20a%20special%20rule%20called%20the%20%26quot%3Bpossession%20holding%20period.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECole%20explained%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bpossession%20holding%20period%26quot%3B%20is%20the%20key%20and%20means%20that%20only%20gains%20made%20while%20living%20in%20Puerto%20Rico%20are%20exempt%20from%20the%20US%20capital%20gains%20tax.%20She%20noted%20that%20this%20is%20also%20true%20for%20those%20who%20qualify%20for%20citizenship%20for%20the%20entire%20year%2C%20but%20only%20lived%20on%20the%20island%20for%20a%20portion%20of%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Sean%20Flynn%20and%20Sarah%20Lindsey%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretire-puerto-rico-tax-benefits-healthcare-residency-requirements-real-estate-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esemi-retired%20couple%20who%20moved%20from%20Texas%20to%20Puerto%20Rico%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20that%20means%20keeping%20a%20detailed%20log%20of%20asset%20values%20before%20they%20moved%20and%20how%20much%20they%20have%20changed%20each%20year%20after%20becoming%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20to%20keep%20track%20of%20the%20day%20that%20I%20moved%20here%20and%20the%20gains%20that%20I%20had%20up%20until%20that%20point%2C%26quot%3B%20Flynn%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20if%20I%20sell%20an%20asset%20that%20I%20owned%20before%20I%20moved%2C%20I%20have%20to%20keep%20track%20of%20that%20and%20say%2C%20'Oh%2C%20I%20had%20a%20gain%20that%20was%20not%20while%20I%20lived%20in%20Puerto%20Rico.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20moving%20to%20Puerto%20Rico%2C%20the%20couple%20sold%20their%20condo%20in%20Austin%2C%20a%20move%20that%20was%20not%20exempt%20from%20capital%20gains%20tax.%20However%2C%20the%20condo%20they%20purchased%20on%20the%20island%20after%20moving%20will%20be%20free%20of%20the%20tax%20if%20it%20accrues%20value%20by%20the%20time%20they%20sell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Houses%20in%20Old%20San%20Juan%2C%20Puerto%20Rico.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f99aad895d822030323037%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221668%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHouses%20in%20Old%20San%20Juan%2C%20Puerto%20Rico.%3Cp%3EOscar%20Gutierrez%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Cole%2C%20another%20misunderstanding%20is%20income%20tax%20and%20what%20is%20eligible%20for%20the%20lower%20rate.%20Similar%20to%20the%20capital%20gains%20tax%20exemption%2C%20only%20income%20from%20sources%20within%20Puerto%20Rico%20qualify%20for%20the%20lower%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20is%20true%20for%20income%20derived%20from%20a%20business%20being%20operated%20in%20the%20US%20territory.%20The%20lower%20tax%20rate%20only%20pertains%20to%20income%20received%20for%20services%20exported%20from%20Puerto%20Rico.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20are%20some%20gray%20areas%20that%20people%20may%20seek%20to%20avoid%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20being%20safe.%20For%20example%2C%20Flynn%2C%20who%20owns%20an%20IT%20consulting%20business%2C%20AFI%20Technologies%2C%20has%20been%20advised%20that%20if%20he%20conducts%20business%20while%20visiting%20the%2050%20states%2C%20that%20could%20be%20viewed%20as%20a%20service%20not%20exported%20from%20Puerto%20Rico%20and%20therefore%20not%20applicable%20for%20the%20lower%20income%20tax%20rate%20even%20those%20his%20business%20is%20registered%20on%20the%20island.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20tax%20incentives%20are%20designed%20to%20lure%20the%20wealthy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tax%20breaks%20are%20nice%2C%20but%20not%20everybody%20can%20afford%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECole%20said%20that%20another%20rule%20that%20often%20surprises%20people%20is%20they%20can't%20claim%20the%20tax%20breaks%20if%20they%20have%20previously%20lived%20on%20the%20island%2C%20moved%20away%2C%20and%20returned%20within%2010%20years.%20Additionally%2C%20those%20seeking%20tax%20breaks%20must%20give%20%2410%2C000%20annually%20to%20specific%20Puerto%20Rico-based%20charities%20and%20purchase%20a%20residence%20on%20the%20island%20within%20two%20years%20of%20moving%20to%20Puerto%20Rico.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Condos%20in%20Condado%2C%20Puerto%20Rico%2C%20are%20popular%20with%20wealthy%20mainlanders.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f99a4a2417f97b87cd4962%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECondos%20in%20Condado%2C%20Puerto%20Rico%2C%20are%20popular%20with%20wealthy%20mainlanders.%3Cp%3ESanghwan%20Kim%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20latter%20two%20requirements%20help%20ensure%20that%20those%20seeking%20the%20tax%20breaks%20have%20higher%20net%20worths%20to%20contribute%20to%20Puerto%20Rico's%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAct%2060%20was%20designed%20to%20promote%20economic%20growth%20in%20Puerto%20Rico%20by%20encouraging%20foreigners%20to%20move%20to%20the%20island%20for%20extended%20periods%20of%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Cole%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20therefore%20designed%20to%20benefit%20the%20Puerto%20Rican%20economy%20the%20most%20and%20is%20structured%20to%20attract%20those%20more%20likely%20to%20positively%20impact%20the%20local%20economy%20to%20relocate%20to%20the%20island.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWith%20the%20tax%20breaks%20comes%20extra%20scrutiny%20from%20the%20IRS%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20downside%2C%20according%20to%20Cole%2C%20is%20the%20same%20people%20the%20island%20is%20trying%20to%20attract%20will%20automatically%20attract%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20IRS.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFocus%20from%20the%20IRS%20often%20begins%20with%20the%20identification%20of%20those%20applying%20for%20Act%2060%20benefits%2C%20filing%20change%20of%20address%20requests%20to%20Puerto%20Rico%2C%20claims%20of%20exemption%2C%20and%20nonfilers%2C%26quot%3B%20Cole%20said.%20She%20added%20that%20once%20somebody%20is%20under%20the%20IRS's%20radar%2C%20investigations%20may%20include%20the%20inspection%20of%20travel%20records%2C%20credit%20card%20purchase%20locations%2C%20and%20income%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20who%20do%20get%20caught%20not%20adhering%20to%20the%20rules%20may%20be%20subjected%20to%20what%20Cole%20described%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20monetary%20and%20criminal%20penalty.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECole%20shared%20a%20common%20piece%20of%20advice%20given%20by%20others%20who%20live%20on%20the%20island%3A%20visit%20the%20island%20ahead%20of%20time%20and%20talk%20to%20people%20who%20have%20already%20made%20the%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20she%20also%20added%20that%20it%20is%20important%20to%20speak%20with%20tax%20professionals%20on%20the%20mainland%20and%20in%20Puerto%20Rico%20so%20that%20there%20are%20no%20surprises.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20moved%20to%20Puerto%20Rico%