bka-saath-sabka-vikas-hoax%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPart%20V%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fevms-and-vvpats-why-the-suspicions-will-not-abate-yet%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPart%20VI%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthe-indian-railways-hype-and-reality%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPart%20VII%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20supreme%20iconoclast%2C%20Howard%20Zinn%20observed%20that%20there%20is%20no%20such%20thing%20as%20impartial%20history.%20Even%20the%20most%20conscientious%20historians%20are%20partial%20in%20two%20ways%3B%20they%20pick%20and%20choose%20from%20the%20bewildering%20array%20of%20happenings%20from%20the%20past%20and%20their%20interpretation%20is%20influenced%20by%20their%20world%20view%20and%20the%20times%20they%20live%20in.%20Yet%20no%20serious%20historian%20will%20disagree%20that%20the%20sanctity%20of%20facts%20is%20fundamental%20to%20any%20historical%20endeavour.%20The%20first%20commandment%20for%20any%20student%20of%20history%20is%20to%20say%20it%20like%20it%20is%2C%20to%20distinguish%20between%20established%20fact%20and%20fiction.%20Arguably%20the%20greatest%20historian%20of%20our%20age%2C%20Eric%20Hobsbawm%2C%20put%20it%20blandly%3A%20%E2%80%9CWithout%20the%20distinction%20of%20what%20is%20and%20what%20is%20not%20so%2C%20there%20can%20be%20no%20history.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20pitfall%20to%20watch%20out%20for%20is%20what%20Hobsbawm%20calls%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20politico-ideological%20abuse%20of%20history%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20warped%20nationalist%20version%20that%20is%20nothing%20short%20of%20a%20bastardisation%20of%20history%20based%20on%20myth%2C%20omission%2C%20decontextualisation%20and%20lies%2C%20with%20the%20past%20serving%20as%20handmaid%20to%20legitimise%20and%20validate%20extreme%20right-wing%20ideologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20300px)%2085vw%2C%20300px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F03150954%2FPrism.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F03150954%2FPrism.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F03150954%2FPrism-150x150.png%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-691446%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%3EHistorical%20research%20and%20writing%20have%20hitherto%20worked%20in%20the%20shadows%2C%20perceived%20as%20relatively%20benign%20scholarly%20activity%20that%20was%20far%20removed%20from%20the%20hurly-burly%20of%20politics.%20But%20today%20the%20past%20is%20being%20invoked%20as%20grist%20for%20nationalist%20and%20fundamental%20ideologies%20just%20%E2%80%9Cas%20poppies%20are%20the%20raw%20material%20for%20heroin%20addicts%E2%80%9D.%20What%E2%80%99s%20being%20peddled%20is%20propaganda%2C%20not%20history.%20The%20autocrats%20of%20our%20present-day%20world%20seem%20to%20draw%20inspiration%20from%20George%20Orwell%E2%80%99s%20dark%20hypothesis%3A%20%E2%80%9CThose%20who%20control%20the%20present%2C%20control%20the%20past%20and%20those%20who%20control%20the%20past%2C%20control%20the%20future.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20now%20direct%2C%20unabashed%20political%20engagement%20with%20historiography.%20For%20the%20cynical%20fantasy%20historians%20of%20the%20present%20regime%2C%20their%20ideology%20of%20exclusivity%20is%20immutable%3B%20history%20must%20be%20recalibrated%20to%20correspond%20with%20their%20beliefs%20and%20socio-political%20agenda%2C%20and%20to%20hell%20with%20facts.%20According%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Finvestigates%2Fspecial-report%2Findia-modi-culture%2F%5C%22%3E2018%20Reuters%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20this%20government%20has%20appointed%20a%20committee%20of%20scholars%20whose%20mandate%20is%20to%20harness%20evidence%20in%20the%20form%20of%20archaeological%20evidence%20and%20DNA%20to%20prove%20that%20Hindus%20are%20the%20original%20inhabitants%20of%20this%20land%2C%20that%20the%20Hindu%20scriptures%20are%20facts%20and%20not%20myth%2C%20that%20there%20is%20a%20foundational%20animus%20between%20Hindu%20and%20Muslim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20%E2%80%93%20mischievous%20to%20the%20extreme%20%E2%80%93%20aims%20to%20debunk%20the%20authenticated%20hopeful%2C%20humane%20narrative%20of%20a%20multicultural%20ethos%20germinated%20in%20migrations%2C%20invasions%20and%20conversions.%20The%20frightful%20objective%20of%20the%20exercise%20is%20to%20justify%20the%20ideological%20fascism%20of%20Hindutva%20that%20demonises%20minorities%20and%20consigns%20them%20to%20the%20margins%20as%20enemies%20of%20the%20nation.%20The%20cultural%20erasure%20of%20minorities%20is%20now%20state%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrejudice%20masquerading%20as%20history%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20traction%20today.%20Orwell%20who%20had%20studied%20the%20innards%20of%20nationalism%20and%20its%20extreme%20manifestation%20%E2%80%93%20fascism%20%E2%80%93%20believed%20that%20the%20nationalist%20is%20%E2%80%9Chaunted%20by%20the%20belief%20that%20the%20past%20can%20be%20altered%E2%80%9D%20and%20so%20rewrites%20history%20that%20is%20%E2%80%9Cplain%20forgery%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthoritarian%20leaders%20across%20the%20world%20have%20been%20presiding%20over%20the%20calculated%20desecration%20of%20history.%20As%20US%20president%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20who%20never%20tired%20of%20excoriating%20academia%20for%20highlighting%20slavery%20and%20racism%20in%20school%20texts%2C%20set%20up%20a%20fresh%201776%20Commission%20to%20%E2%80%9Cpromote%20patriotic%20education%E2%80%9D%20with%20the%20intent%20of%20rewriting%20history%20to%20suit%20the%20purposes%20of%20his%20right-wing%2C%20racist%20constituency.%20The%20Commission%20submitted%20its%20report%20%E2%80%93%20chockfull%20of%20falsehoods%20and%20partisan%20politics%20%E2%80%93%20two%20days%20before%20the%20end%20of%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20term%20in%202020%20but%20thankfully%2C%20neither%20the%20Commission%20nor%20its%20mischievous%20historical%20fiction%20survived%20his%20presidency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20not%20been%20so%20lucky.%20The%20jaundiced%20world%20view%20of%20the%20hyper-nationalists%20wielding%20political%20power%20has%20muscled%20its%20way%20into%20education%20and%20school%20textbooks%2C%20poisoning%20the%20minds%20of%20the%20most%20vulnerable.%20Adopting%20the%20laziest%20and%20crudest%20form%20of%20falsification%2C%20the%20NCERT%20(National%20Council%20for%20Education%20Research%20and%20Training)%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fncert-history-textbooks-mughals-india%5C%22%3Evandalised%20the%20history%20syllabus%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20schools%20by%20blanking%20out%20large%20parts%20of%20%E2%80%9CMuslim%20history%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20Gujarat%20massacre%20of%202002%20and%20anything%20inimical%20to%20the%20Hindutva%20view%20of%20history.%20The%20BJP-ruled%20states%20have%20also%20got%20into%20the%20act%20of%20revising%20history%20texts%2C%20sometimes%20with%20the%20most%20comical%20outcomes.%20During%20BJP%20rule%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20history%20textbooks%20were%20revised%20and%20glorified%20Savarkar%2C%20stating%2C%20inter%20alia%2C%20the%20tripe%20that%20during%20his%20incarceration%20in%20the%20Cellular%20jail%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbulbul%20birds%20used%20to%20visit%20the%20room%20and%20Savarkar%20used%20to%20sit%20on%20their%20wings%20and%20fly%20out%20and%20visit%20the%20motherland%20every%20day%E2%80%9D.%20The%20irrepressible%20Aakar%20Patel%20said%20it%20for%20us%20when%20he%20wryly%20tweeted%3A%20%E2%80%9CAlways%20knew%20he%20was%20a%20lightweight.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20truly%20scandalous%20is%20the%20willingness%20of%20the%20scientific%20community%20to%20actively%20abet%20this%20multi-pronged%20assault%20on%20our%20history%2C%20although%20its%20shameless%20embrace%20of%20this%20regime%E2%80%99s%20ludicrous%20claims%20about%20our%20ancient%20past%20has%20severely%20damaged%20its%20credibility.%20During%20the%20106th%20session%20of%20the%20Indian%20Science%20Congress%20in%202019%2C%20presided%20over%20by%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20prime%20minister%2C%20the%20most%20bizarre%20claims%20were%20made%20about%20our%20ancient%20past%20%E2%80%93%20that%20India%20was%20making%20test-tube%20babies%20and%20familiar%20with%20plastic%20surgery%20thousands%20of%20years%20ago%3B%20ancient%20India%20was%20familiar%20with%20internet%20and%20nuclear%20weapons%3B%20India%20has%20given%20the%20world%20the%20Pythagoras%E2%80%99s%20theorem%3B%20there%20were%20planes%20in%20the%20Vedic%20age%20that%20journeyed%20across%20planets.%20Is%20it%20a%20coincidence%20that%20in%20Orwell%E2%80%99s%20surreal%20tale%20of%20totalitarianism%2C%20%3Cem%3ENineteen%20Eighty-four%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethere%20is%20this%20postulation%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Party%E2%80%99s%20history%20books%20claimed%20that%20the%20Party%20had%20invented%20aeroplanes%E2%80%9D%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20today%E2%80%99s%20India%20of%20oppressive%20iniquity%2C%20can%20the%20judiciary%20be%20far%20behind%3F%20%C2%A0The%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20tacit%20endorsement%20of%20this%20regime%E2%80%99s%20erasure%20of%20relics%20relating%20to%20inconvenient%20facets%20of%20history%20is%20evident%20in%20its%20shocking%20verdict%20of%20July%202020%20on%20petitions%20seeking%20protection%20of%20ancient%20remains%20and%20artifacts%20recovered%20during%20excavation%20of%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20site%20for%20construction%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20striking%20example%20of%20the%20highest%20court%20abetting%20%E2%80%9Cspoliation%20of%20evidence%E2%80%9D%2C%20an%20eminently%20reasonable%20plea%20for%20conserving%20relics%20found%20at%20the%20historically%20contentious%20archaeological%20site%20%E2%80%93%20a%20routine%2C%20indispensable%20exercise%20for%20a%20country%20that%20values%20its%20cultural%20heritage%20%E2%80%93%20was%20dismissed%20as%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fsc-dismisses-pleas-for-preserving-artefacts-found-at-ram-janmabhoomi%2Farticle61681886.ece%5C%22%3Eabsolutely%20frivolous%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D.%20The%20three-judge%20bench%20headed%20by%20who%20else%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fjustice-arun-mishra-judgments-analysis%5C%22%3EArun%20Mishra%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20sycophantic%20%E2%80%9Cthinking%20globally%20but%20acting%20locally%E2%80%9D%20fame%2C%20pulled%20up%20and%20imposed%20costs%20on%20the%20petitioners%20for%20questioning%2C%20by%20inference%2C%20the%20bizarre%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fayodhya-verdict-supreme-court-full-text%5C%22%3E2019%20Supreme%20Court%20Ayodhya%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%3C%2Fa%3E%20verdict%20which%20privileged%20faith%20over%20the%20law%2C%20even%20implying%20that%20the%20Ayodhya%20judgment%20cannot%20be%20questioned%20even%20in%20its%20historical%20context.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ongoing%20root-and-branch%20cooking%20and%20rewriting%20of%20our%20history%2C%20the%20forced%20imposition%20of%20a%20dubious%20Hindu%20nationalist%20narrative%20into%20our%20understanding%20of%20the%20past%2C%20could%20not%20have%20been%20possible%20without%20the%20imprimatur%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20the%20all-powerful%20talisman%20of%20Hindutva.%20A%20post-graduate%20in%20%E2%80%9CEntire%20Political%20Science%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20has%20mastered%20the%20high-sounding%20rhetoric%20of%20grievance%2C%20decolonisation%20and%20democratisation%20to%20denigrate%20the%20%E2%80%9Celitist%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cleftist%E2%80%9D%20dominance%20of%20historiography.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202021%2C%20at%20a%20function%20commemorating%20the%20Dalit%20chieftain%20Maharaj%20Suheldev%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fpm-modi-lays-foundation-stone-for-warrior-king-suheldevs-statue-in-ups-bahraich%2Farticle33848574.ece%5C%22%3Elashed%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20distortions%20perpetrated%20by%20those%20who%20enslaved%20the%20country%20and%20the%20elitist%20colonised%20minds%20who%20have%20since%20dominated%20the%20historical%20discourse.%20He%20bemoaned%20the%20neglect%20of%20heroes%20who%20dedicated%20their%20lives%20to%20the%20protection%20of%20%E2%80%9CBharatiyata%E2%80%9D%20which%20essentially%20is%20Hindutva%20without%20its%20abrasive%20resonance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIronically%2C%20his%20polemic%20is%20an%20appropriated%20perversion%20of%20Ranajit%20Guha%E2%80%99s%20exposition%20on%20colonial%20expropriation%20of%20our%20history%20that%20has%20largely%20ignored%20the%20subaltern%20perspective%20i.e.%20the%20commoner.%20The%20essential%20difference%20is%20that%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20alternate%20%E2%80%9Cguaranteed%E2%80%9D%20history%20seeks%20to%20validate%20an%20exclusive%2C%20sectarian%20Hindu%20ethos%20and%20culture%20that%20erases%20or%20belittles%20anything%20Muslim%2C%20a%20blasphemous%20distortion%20would%20make%20Guha%20turn%20in%20his%20grave.%20Leaving%20no%20doubt%20about%20his%20government%E2%80%99s%20intentions%20of%20rewriting%20history%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20declared%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20injustice%20and%20tampering%20(of%20history)%20done%20hitherto%20is%20being%20rectified%20today%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20historical%20misrepresentation%20by%20this%20regime%2C%20one%20cannot%20ignore%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20ahistorical%20denigration%20of%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20the%20contentious%20Kashmir%20issue.%20Modi%20and%20his%20ilk%20peddle%20the%20cock%20and%20bull%20story%20that%20whereas%20Sardar%20Patel%20deftly%20manoeuvred%20the%20merger%20of%20the%20princely%20states%2C%20Nehru%20botched%20the%20handling%20of%20Kashmir%20by%20agreeing%20to%20a%20plebiscite%20and%20the%20enactment%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20a%20troublesome%20burden%20that%20Modi%20finally%20resolved.%20To%20quote%20his%20braggadocio%20in%202022%3A%20%E2%80%9CAs%20I%20am%20following%20the%20footsteps%20of%20Sardar%20Saheb%2C%20%E2%80%A6I%20resolved%20the%20problem%20of%20Kashmir%20and%20paid%20true%20tributes%20to%20Sardar%20Patel.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajmohan%20Gandhi%2C%20arguably%20our%20finest%20historian%20on%20the%20Independence%20movement%2C%20has%20clinically%20torn%20apart%20the%20specious%20argument%20that%20Patel%20would%20have%20ensured%20the%20transfer%20of%20Kashmir%20in%20its%20entirety%20to%20India%20but%20for%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20pusillanimity.%20The%20historical%20record%20notes%20that%20Patel%20had%20come%20to%20terms%20with%20Kashmir%20being%20handed%20over%20to%20Pakistan%20until%20September%201947%2C%20when%20Junagarh%20announced%20its%20accession%20to%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20not%20forget%20that%20by%20the%20logic%20of%20Partition%2C%20the%20Kashmir%20valley%20abutting%20Pakistan%20and%20with%20an%20overwhelming%20Muslim%20population%20(93%25)%20should%20logically%20have%20gone%20to%20Pakistan.%20As%20M.J.%20Akbar%20reveals%20in%20his%20brilliant%20biography%20of%20Nehru%2C%20the%20first%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20unwavering%20determination%20to%20hold%20on%20to%20Kashmir%20was%20why%20we%20got%20Kashmir%2C%20despite%20the%20inclination%20of%20the%20British%20to%20favour%20Pakistan.%20According%20to%20Mountbatten%2C%20Kashmir%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpathological%E2%80%9D%20obsession%20for%20Nehru%20whose%20friendship%20with%20Mountbatten%20and%20Sheikh%20Abdullah%20ensured%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20claim%20to%20Kashmir%20prevailed%20against%20all%20odds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENehru%E2%80%99s%20detractors%20lament%20that%20when%20the%20Indian%20Army%2C%20having%20driven%20out%20the%20Pathan%20raiders%2C%20was%20poised%20to%20occupy%20POK%20and%20settle%20the%20Kashmir%20issue%20once%20and%20for%20all%2C%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20meek%20acceptance%20of%20a%20plebiscite%20is%20solely%20responsible%20for%20all%20the%20festering%20problems%20of%20Kashmir%20since%20then.%20The%20trouble%20with%20hindsight%20is%20that%20it%20tends%20to%20exaggerate%20and%20embellish%20the%20missed%20opportunity%20and%20downplay%20the%20difficulties%20faced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECritics%20forget%20that%20the%20crisis%20in%20Kashmir%20was%20happening%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20most%20unspeakable%20inhumanity%20and%20crazed%20religious%20frenzy%20on%20either%20side%20of%20the%20border.%20Up%20to%20two%20million%20men%2C%20women%20and%20children%20were%20butchered%20and%2020%20million%20displaced%20in%20the%20holocaust%20of%20Partition.%20At%20such%20a%20grim%20time%2C%20it%20would%20have%20been%20suicidal%20to%20embark%20on%20a%20full-scale%20war%20with%20Pakistan%20which%20would%20have%20further%20inflamed%20communal%20passions.%20Sadly%2C%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20India%2C%20the%20bigoted%20narrative%20of%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20critics%20holds%20sway!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20in%20the%20grip%20of%20a%20majoritarian%20nationalist%20government%20that%20is%20hell-bent%20on%20tearing%20apart%20the%20idea%20of%20India%20conceived%20by%20our%20founding%20fathers.%20Having%20coopted%20most%20institutions%20of%20governance%2C%20it%20is%20perilously%20close%20to%20achieving%20its%20ultimate%20objective%20of%20a%20Hindu%20%3Cem%3Erashtra%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20brazen%20falsification%20of%20history%20is%20a%20crucial%20element%20in%20this%20diabolical%20project.%20Trapped%20in%20this%20oppressive%20social%20milieu%2C%20we%20need%20to%20heed%20Orwell%E2%80%99s%20warning%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20most%20effective%20way%20to%20destroy%20people%20is%20to%20deny%20and%20obliterate%20their%20own%20understanding%20of%20their%20history.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20a%20change%20of%20regime%20in%20June%202024%20can%20pull%20us%20back%20from%20the%20brink!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMathew%20John%20is%20a%20former%20civil%20servant%20and%20Annie%20Mathew%20teaches%20history.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710927030000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2F30134823%2FIMG_2578.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fa-land-where-prejudice-masquerades-as-history%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ongoing%20root-and-branch%20cooking%20and%20rewriting%20of%20our%20history%2C%20the%20forced%20imposition%20of%20a%20dubious%20Hindu%20nationalist%20narrative%20into%20our%20understanding%20of%20the%20past%2C%20could%20not%20have%20been%20possible%20without%20the%20imprimatur%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fa-land-where-prejudice-masquerades-as-history%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCan't%20Keep%20Filing%20Chargesheets%20To%20Keep%20People%20In%20Jail%26quot%3B%2C%20Top%20Court%20Observes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fsupreme-court%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20questioned%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20over%20filing%20of%20supplementary%20charge%20sheets%20to%20deny%20default%20bail%20for%20an%20accused%2C%20and%20to%20keep%20such%20persons%20in%20jail%20for%20an%20indefinite%20period.%20A%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20and%20Justice%20Dipankar%20Datta%20told%20the%20central%20agency%20this%20practice%20-%20of%20effectively%20keeping%20accused%20in%20jail%20without%20a%20trial%20-%20troubled%20the%20top%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20object%20of%20default%20bail%20is%20that%20you%20do%20not%20arrest%20(an%20accused)%20till%20the%20investigation%20is%20complete.%20You%20cannot%20(arrest%20an%20accused%20and)%20say%20the%20trial%20will%20not%20commence%20till%20investigation%20is%20not%20complete.%20You%20cannot%20keep%20filing%20supplementary%20charge%20sheets%20and%20then%20the%20person%20is%20in%20jail%20without%20a%20trial%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Khanna%20told%20Additional%20Solicitor-General%20SV%20Raju%2C%20who%20was%20appearing%20for%20the%20ED.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20this%20case%2C%20the%20person%20is%20behind%20bars%20for%2018%20months.%20This%20is%20bothering%20us.%20In%20some%20case%20we%20will%20take%20it%20up%20and%20we%20are%20putting%20you%20to%20notice%20in%20that.%20Trial%20has%20to%20be%20begin%20when%20you%20arrest%20an%20accused%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20current%20laws%20an%20arrested%20individual%20is%20eligible%20for%20default%20bail%20if%20the%20authorities%20are%20unable%20to%20complete%20the%20investigation%2C%20or%20file%20a%20final%20charge%20sheet%2C%20within%20timelines%20set%20by%20the%20CrPC%2C%20or%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure.%20This%20time%20period%20is%20either%2060%20or%2090%20days%2C%20depending%20on%20case%20circumstances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20made%20a%20similar%20observation%20in%20April%20last%20year%3B%20a%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Krishna%20Murari%20and%20Justice%20CT%20Ravikumar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWithout%20completing%20investigation%2C%20a%20charge%20sheet%20cannot%20be%20filed%20by%20an%20investigating%20agency%20only%20to%20deprive%20an%20arrested%20accused%20of%20his%20right%20to%20default%20bail...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcant-file-charge-sheet-without-completing-investigation-supreme-court-3982425%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECan't%20File%20Charge%20Sheet%20Without%20Finishing%20Investigation%3A%20Top%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court's%20crucial%20observation%20could%20go%20on%20to%20impact%20several%20high-profile%20figures%2C%20including%20opposition%20political%20leaders%20who%20have%20been%20arrested%20by%20the%20probe%20agency%20and%20remain%20in%20jail%2C%20facing%20multiple%20charges%20and%20charge%20sheets%20without%20either%20proceeding%20to%20a%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20made%20this%20observation%20while%20hearing%20a%20bail%20plea%20filed%20by%20an%20accused%20linked%20to%20an%20illegal%20mining%20case%20from%20Jharkhand.%20The%20accused%20-%20Prem%20Prakash%20-%20is%20an%20alleged%20aide%20of%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Hemant%20Soren%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20ED%20last%20month%20on%20money-laundering%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Prakash%20was%20denied%20bail%20by%20the%20Jharkhand%20High%20Court%20in%20January%20last%20year.%20He%20had%20then%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20noted%20he%20had%20spent%2018%20months%20in%20jail%20and%20called%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bclear%20case%20of%20bail%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20this%20Mr%20Raju%20raised%20concerns%20of%20evidence%20or%20witness%20tampering%20if%20the%20accused%20were%20released%2C%20but%20the%20court%20was%20not%20convinced.%20%26quot%3BYou%20come%20to%20us%20if%20he%20(Mr%20Prakash)%20does%20any%20of%20that...%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Khanna%20told%20the%20probe%20agency's%20lawyer%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3B...%20but%2018%20months%20behind%20bars%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20noted%20that%20right%20to%20bail%20due%20to%20prolonged%20jail%2C%20under%20Section%2045%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%2C%20or%20PMLA%2C%20could%20be%20granted%20if%20there%20is%20prima%20facie%20belief%20the%20accused%20did%20not%20commit%20the%20offence%2C%20and%20that%20he%20is%20not%20likely%20to%20transgress%20any%20laws%20while%20out%20on%20bail.%20This%2C%20the%20court%20held%2C%20flowed%20from%20Article%2021%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20which%20talks%20about%20right%20to%20personal%20liberty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20referred%20to%20the%20incarceration%20of%20senior%20AAP%20leader%20and%20former%20Delhi%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanish-sisodia-arrested-by-enforcement-directorate-day-before-bail-hearing-3847018%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EManish%20Sisodia%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20ED%20in%20the%20liquor%20policy%20case%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20February%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%20the%20court%20-%20a%20bench%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20and%20including%20Justice%20Khanna%20-%20dismissed%20a%20curative%20petition%20filed%20by%20Mr%20Sisodia%20after%20his%20bail%20plea%20was%20rejected%20in%20October.%20The%20court%20held%20the%20allegations%20-%20of%20%26quot%3Bwindfall%20gains%26quot%3B%20of%20Rs%20338%20crore%20was%20%26quot%3Btentatively%20supported%26quot%3B%20by%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-rejects-manish-sisodias-curative-petition-seeking-bail-in-delhi-liquor-policy-scam-5240058%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%20Rejects%20Manish%20Sisodia's%20Curative%20Petition%20Seeking%20Bail%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoting%20the%20accused%20in%20this%20case%20had%20spent%2018%20months%20in%20jail%2C%20the%20court%20said%20%26quot%3Bconstitutional%20right%20(under%20Article%2021)%20is%20not%20taken%20away%20by%20Section%2045%20(of%20PMLA)...%20this%20is%20very%20clear%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20in%20the%20case%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fmanish-sisodia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EManish%20Sisodia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20said%20default%20bail%20is%20something%20separate.%20If%20there%20is%20delay%20in%20trial%2C%20power%20of%20court%20to%20grant%20bail%20is%20not%20taken%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Khanna%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court's%20observations%20on%20default%20bail%20and%20supplementary%20charge%20sheets%20come%20amid%20allegations%20by%20the%20opposition%20that%20central%20agencies%20like%20the%20ED%20and%20the%20Cen