nd%20we%20signed%20off%20power%20of%20attorney%20to%20them%20for%20our%20first%20Spanish%20property.%20Then%2C%20we%20returned%20to%20the%20States%20and%20owned%20the%20property%20within%20a%20month.%20We're%20lucky%20to%20have%20found%20a%20great%20lawyer%2C%20which%20is%20necessary%20for%20due%20diligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20was%20surprised%20to%20purchase%20two%20properties%20so%20quickly%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20first%20property%20was%20an%20almost%20800-square-foot%20condo%20with%20two%20bedrooms%20and%20one%20bathroom%20in%20a%20fantastic%20and%20convenient%20location%20close%20to%20the%20center%20of%20town.%20Condos%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famericans-moving-to-europe-cheaper-homes-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehomes%20in%20Europe%3C%2Fa%3E%20tend%20to%20be%20much%20smaller%20than%20in%20the%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20purchased%20the%20second%20property%20for%20%24200%2C000%20almost%20a%20year%20after%20arriving.%20We%20weren't%20planning%20to%20buy%20another%20home%2C%20but%20our%20real-estate%20agent%20showed%20us%20this%20gorgeous%20loft-style%20condo%20with%20high%20ceilings%20and%20exposed%20concrete%20beans%20%E2%80%94%20everything%20we%20love.%20It's%20just%20over%201%2C000%20square%20feet%20with%20two%20bedrooms%2C%20two%20bathrooms%2C%20and%20a%20cute%20inner%20courtyard.%20We%20moved%20into%20this%20second%20one%2C%20and%20we're%20working%20on%20renting%20out%20the%20first%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20main%20room%20with%20dining%20table%2C%20sitting%20area%2C%20and%20outdoor%20space.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f988284af076d3cf919325%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELeong%20and%20her%20husband%20moved%20into%20their%20800-square-foot%20condo.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20May%20Leong%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwise.com%2Fus%2Fblog%2Fbuy-property-in-spain%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eany%20American%20is%20allowed%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20buy%20a%20home%20in%20Spain%2C%20you%20may%20need%20to%20apply%20for%20a%20visa%20if%20you%20plan%20to%20live%20there.%20I%20got%20residency%20through%20my%20husband%20because%20he's%20an%20Irish%20EU%20citizen.%20Although%20our%20neighborhood%20is%20filled%20mostly%20with%20local%20Spaniards%2C%20various%20ex-pats%20of%20different%20nationalities%20(Dutch%2C%20Ukrainian%2C%20Italian%2C%20French%2C%20Americans%2C%20and%20British)%20live%20in%20surrounding%20neighborhoods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20more%20Americans%20purchase%20properties%20in%20Spain%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F03%2F17%2Frealestate%2Feurope-homes-sale-americans-lisbon-barcelona.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egentrification%20has%20become%3C%2Fa%3E%20an%20issue%2C%20raising%20housing%20prices.%20I%20believe%20in%20buying%20property%20to%20live%20here%20and%20contribute%20to%20the%20community%20instead%20of%20simply%20purchasing%20property%20as%20an%20ex-pat%20as%20an%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20purchasing%20property%20in%20Spain%2C%20you%20must%20be%20careful%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222710%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22May%20Leong%20taking%20tea%20into%20the%20terrace%20area.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f99aac4af076d3cf919987%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222033%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELeong%20taking%20tea%20into%20her%20terrace%20area.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20May%20Leong%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20tricky%20part%20of%20the%20homebuying%20process%20in%20Spain%20is%20that%20it%20can%20be%20murky%20and%20confusing.%20Sometimes%2C%20when%20we%20spoke%20to%20one%20person%20in%20a%20city%20office%2C%20we'd%20get%20different%20answers%20when%20talking%20to%20a%20different%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckily%2C%20the%20real%20estate%20agents%20we%20worked%20with%20were%20highly%20reputable.%20Purchasing%20a%20property%20is%20a%20considerable%20investment%2C%20and%20it's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feuroweeklynews.com%2F2022%2F10%2F25%2Fexpats-in-spain-warned-as-mum-and-son-left-homeless-after-e320k-home-sold-for-e28k-in-property-scam%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enot%20uncommon%20to%20get%20scammed%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20buying%20in%20a%20different%20country.%20We%20found%20great%20local%20expat%20Facebook%20groups%20to%20learn%20about%20the%20local%20community%20and%20to%20get%20advice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20purchasing%20property%20in%20Spain%2C%20you%20must%20be%20careful.%20You%20might%20find%20a%20great%20home%2C%20but%20when%20you%20look%20closely%20at%20the%20paperwork%2C%20it's%20not%20coded%20or%20approved%20as%20a%20residence.%20We%20were%20warned%20about%20this%20from%20various%20sources%3A%20Facebook%20groups%2C%20our%20real%20estate%20agency%2C%20and%20our%20lawyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOverall%2C%20we%20prefer%20Valencia%20to%20Oakland%20for%20several%20reasons%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22May%20Leong%20and%20her%20husband%20posing%20in%20front%20of%20an%20outdoor%20Christmas%20tree%20in%20Valencia.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f99f40895d8220303232e7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELeong%20and%20her%20husband%20pose%20in%20front%20of%20an%20outdoor%20Christmas%20tree%20in%20Valencia.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20May%20Leong%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EValencia%20has%20a%20lower%20cost%20of%20living%2C%20great%20weather%2C%20less%20crime%2C%20and%20great%20food%20and%20drinks.%20We%20can%20walk%20almost%20everywhere%20and%20anywhere%20in%20the%20city%20day%20and%20night%20and%20aren't%20worried%20about%20being%20mugged%20or%20assaulted.%20We%20miss%20having%20friends%20and%20family%20and%20access%20to%20great%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-5-best-chinese-restaurants-in-the-bay-area-2012-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChinese%20food%20in%20Oakland%20and%20the%20Bay%20Area%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Most%20of%20the%20Chinese%20restaurants%20in%20Valencia%20haven't%20been%20great%2C%20but%20we%20still%20prefer%20living%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EValencia%20is%20also%20Spain's%20third-largest%20city%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20very%20urban.%20The%20attraction%20of%20moving%20to%20Valencia%20was%20being%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20city.%20Just%20outside%20our%20door%20are%20caf%C3%A9s%20and%20restaurants%20that%20close%20at%202%20a.m.%20We%20love%20our%20lives%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-to-spain-from-california-retired-home-buying-process-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710925982000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65fa332f4af076d3cf91d5fc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-to-spain-from-california-retired-home-buying-process-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20home%20buying%20process%20in%20Spain%20was%20faster%20and%20easier%20than%20the%20US%2C%20says%20a%20retired%20American%20couple%20who%20moved%20from%20California.%20They%20plan%20to%20stay.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Kaila%20Yu)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-to-spain-from-california-retired-home-buying-process-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK%20inflation%20slows%20to%20lowest%20level%20in%20almost%202.5%20years%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710925829000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108645301%2Cimgsize-624858.cms%2