%20Batra%E2%80%99s%20Right%20to%20Information%20(RTI)%20query.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20bonds%20worth%20Rs%208%2C350%20crores%20printed%20this%20year%20are%20more%20than%20what%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20has%20amassed%20through%20the%20scheme%20since%20its%20inception.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20data%20published%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fhow-much-money-did-the-bjp-really-get-from-electoral-bonds%5C%22%3EBJP%20has%20received%20Rs%208%2C251.8%20crores%20in%20electoral%20bonds%20since%202018.%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20total%20value%20of%20bonds%20sold%20in%20this%20period%20is%20Rs%2016%2C518%20crore.%20This%20means%20the%20BJP%20redeemed%20about%2050%25%20of%20all%20bonds%20sold.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fflo.uri.sh%2Fvisualisation%2F17197297%2Fembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Interactive%20or%20visual%20content%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20earlier%20RTI%20filed%20by%20Batra%20had%20established%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Felectoral-bonds-tax-payers-cost-printing-bank-commission%5C%22%3Etaxpayer%2C%20not%20the%20donors%20or%20political%20parties%2C%20is%20footing%20the%20bill%20of%20printing%20and%20managing%20electoral%20bonds.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESBI%2C%20the%20bank%20authorised%20to%20issue%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20had%20charged%20Rs%2013.50%20crore%20to%20the%20government%20towards%20its%20%E2%80%9Ccommission%2C%20printing%20and%20other%20expenses%20for%20managing%20and%20operating%20the%20Electoral%20Bonds%20Scheme%2C%E2%80%9D%20between%202018-2023%2C%20the%20RTI%20response%20had%20revealed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20cost%20of%20printing%20and%20managing%20the%20additional%208%2C350%20bonds%20this%20year%20is%20not%20yet%20known.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20appears%20that%20the%20government%20was%20confident%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20would%20maintain%20the%20status%20quo.%20That%20was%20why%20it%20went%20ahead%20with%20printing%20more%20bonds%20of%20Rs%201%20crore%2C%E2%80%9D%20Batra%20told%3Cem%3E%20The%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20February%2015%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-electoral-bonds-quash-anonymous%5C%22%3Estruck%20down%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%3C%2Fa%3E.%20While%20calling%20it%20unconstitutional%20and%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20voters%E2%80%99%20right%20to%20this%20information%2C%20the%20court%20had%20directed%20the%20SBI%20to%20furnish%20the%20details%20of%20the%20bonds%20to%20the%20EC.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710922334000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F20133735%2FScreenshot-2024-03-20-at-1.37.24-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fbjp-govt-printed-ebs-worth-rs-8350-cr-after-sc-reserved-verdict-on-scheme-rti%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20bonds%20worth%20Rs%208%2C350%20crore%20printed%20this%20year%20are%20more%20than%20Rs%208251.8%2C%20or%20what%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20has%20amassed%20through%20the%20scheme%20since%20its%20inception.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fbjp-govt-printed-ebs-worth-rs-8350-cr-after-sc-reserved-verdict-on-scheme-rti%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kareena%20Kapoor%20Khan%20praises%20'Madgaon%20Express'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710922061000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108642230%2Cimgsize-82228.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkareena-kapoor-khan-pra