0Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20his%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20from%20claiming%20a%20third%20consecutive%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DMK%20has%20also%20vowed%20to%20scrap%20the%20NEET%2C%20or%20National%20Entrance%20Eligibility%20Test%2C%20which%20is%20administered%20for%20admission%20to%20medical%20courses%20pan-India.%20Tamil%20Nadu%20is%20a%20fierce%20critic%20of%20the%20NEET.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftamil-nadu-news%2Ftamil-nadu-moves-supreme-court-challenging-validity-of-medical-exam-neet-3795564%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETamil%20Nadu%20Moves%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20Challenges%20Validity%20Of%20NEET%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%20last%20year%20the%20state%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20claiming%20the%20single-window%20common%20exam%20is%20violates%20federal%20principles%2C%20since%20it%20takes%20away%20states'%20decision-making%20ability%20regarding%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReleased%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin%20and%20senior%20leaders%2C%20including%20Thoothukudi%20MP%20Kanimozhi%2C%20the%20DMK%20has%20laid%20out%20a%20strong%20agenda%20of%20reviewing%20the%20BJP's%20%26quot%3Banti-people%20laws%26quot%3B%2C%20including%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%2C%20which%20it%20has%20heavily%20criticised%20for%20imposing%20Hindi%20on%20the%20southern%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BPeople's%20Manifesto%26quot%3B%2C%20Says%20Chief%20Minister%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20DMK%20continues%20to%20do%20what%20we%20say...%20this%20is%20what%20our%20leaders%20taught%20us.%20We%20went%20all%20over%20the%20state%20and%20listened%20to%20the%20people.%20This%20is%20not%20just%20a%20DMK%20manifesto...%20it%20is%20the%20people's%20manifesto%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Stalin%20said%2C%20accusing%20the%20BJP%20of%20having%20%26quot%3Bdestroyed%20India%26quot%3B%20and%20failing%20to%20fulfil%20their%20promises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20also%20took%20a%20jab%20at%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20who%20has%20made%20six%20visits%20to%20Tamil%20Nadu%20this%20year.%20Mr%20Stalin%20remarked%20he%20would%20have%20happier%20had%20the%20PM%20%26quot%3Bcome%20during%20the%20time%20of%20floods%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-holds-massive-rally-in-aiadmk-stronghold-salem-in-tamil-nadu-5271135%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPM%20Holds%20Massive%20Rally%20In%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Targets%20AIADMK%20Stronghold%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Modi%20has%20been%20actively%20touring%20the%20southern%20states%20to%20boost%20the%20BJP's%20profile.%20The%20party%20has%20a%20negligible%20presence%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%3B%20in%20the%20last%20election%20it%20got%20less%20than%20three%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EKanimozhi%20To%20NDTV%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDMK%20MP%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fkanimozhi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKanimozhi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20has%20been%20nominated%20to%20defend%20her%20Thoothukudi%20seat%2C%20told%20NDTV%20the%20manifesto%20focused%20on%20protecting%20the%20federal%20nature%20of%20the%20country%20-%20a%20concern%20frequently%20also%20raised%20by%20Bengal's%20Trinamool%2C%20another%20INDIA%20bloc%20member%2C%20and%20the%20rights%20of%20state%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20promises%20are%20implementable%20if%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20forms%20the%20(central)%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20expressing%20thanks%20to%20the%20DMK%20for%20re-fielding%20her%20from%20the%20Thoothukudi%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-kamal-haasan-mk-stalin-congress-india-bloc-congress-dmk-seal-deal-in-tamil-nadu-guest-appearance-by-kamal-haasan-5205485%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECongress-DMK%20Seal%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Deal%2C%20Guest%20Showing%20By%20Kamal%20Haasan%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DMK%20today%20also%20released%20a%20first%20list%20of%20candidates%20for%20the%2021%20seats%20it%20will%20contest%3B%20Tamil%20Nadu%20has%2039%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%20The%20rest%20will%20go%20to%20the%20Congress%20and%20smaller%20parties%2C%20in%20allotments%20identical%20to%20the%202019%20arrangement.%20Five%20years%20ago%20the%20DMK-Congress%20combine%20swept%20the%20state%2C%20winning%2038%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20seen%20how%20much%20the%20Dravidian%20model%20of%20government%20has%20done%20for%20the%20people%20of%20this%20state%2C%20and%20this%20manifesto%20will%20help%20us%20take%20our%20Dravidian%20model%20all%20over%20India.%20I%20am%20sure%20of%20securing%20not%20only%20all%20seats%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20but%20a%20good%20number%20across%20the%20country%20too...%26quot%3B%20Kanimozhi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDMK%20Lok%20Sabha%20Manifesto%20Details%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20other%20big-ticket%20promises%20made%20by%20the%20DMK%20are%20drastic%20cuts%20to%20the%20prices%20of%20petrol%2C%20diesel%2C%20and%20LPG%20(cooking%20gas)%20to%20Rs%2075%20and%20Rs%2065%20per%20litre%20and%20Rs%20500%20per%20cylinder%2C%20free%20Wi-Fi%20services%20across%20the%20state%2C%20statehood%20for%20Puducherry%2C%20scrapping%20of%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%2C%20and%20the%20immediate%20implementation%20of%2033%20per%20cent%20reservation%20for%20women%20in%20Parliament%20and%20state%20legislatures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20a%20focus%20on%20students%20and%20women%20empowerment%20in%20the%20manifesto%2C%20which%20promises%20interest-free%20loans%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%204%20lakh%20for%20students%20and%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20for%20women%20self-help%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%