%20and%20wholeheartedly%20welcome%20this%20new%20launch%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fzomato%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40zomato%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdeepigoyal%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40deepigoyal%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20a%20vegetarian%20who%20orders%20food%20from%20delivery%20services%20atleast%20once%20a%20day%2C%20I%20had%20numerous%20experiences%20of%20being%20sent%20chicken%20rolls%20instead%20of%20veg%2C%20meat%20pieces%20in%20my%20food%2C%20wrong%20orders%20delivered%2C%20etc.%20I%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FT2v5qdOQLz%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FT2v5qdOQLz%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Ricky%20Kej%20(%40rickykej)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frickykej%2Fstatus%2F1770261385496449204%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2020%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kej%2C%20reacting%20to%20Mr%20Goyal's%20statement%2C%20said%20that%20the%20company's%20%26quot%3Bintention%20is%20only%20to%20serve%20people%20with%20dietary%20preferences.%20This%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20caste%2C%20or%20religion.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20argued%20that%20anyone's%20dietary%20preference%20should%20not%20become%20an%20issue.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20funny%20(and%20disaheartening)%20that%20in%20India%2C%20we%20have%20to%20defend%20ourselves%20for%20being%20vegetarian..%20when%20it%20should%20be%20the%20opposite!!%20No%20one%20had%20to%20die%20for%20my%20meal%20or%20my%20snack!!%20Hahah.%20Also%2C%20it%20is%20proven%20time%20and%20again%20that%20a%20meat-free%20diet%20is%20far%20more%20sustainable%20for%20the%20planet.%20This%20is%20a%20dietary%20preference%20and%20a%20personal%20choice.%20That%20is%20all!%20So%20when%20%40zomato%20is%20catering%20to%20our%20needs%2C%20why%20should%20this%20become%20an%20issue%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Goyal%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fdeepi