Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIshwar%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Khajuri%20Bazar%20was%20on%20his%20way%20to%20a%20workshop%20to%20get%20the%20'car%20copter'%20painted%20when%20he%20was%20stopped%20by%20a%20traffic%20policeman%20and%20fined%20for%20his%20unauthorised%20modifications.%20His%20unique%20vehicle%20was%20also%20confiscated%20by%20police%20and%20later%20released%20on%20payment%20of%20the%20fine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIshwar's%20modified%20version%20of%20the%20car%20also%20sports%20the%20tail%20rotor%20of%20a%20chopper%20welded%20to%20the%20boot%20of%20the%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20he%20made%20the%20eye-catching%20customisations%20with%20plans%20to%20lend%20it%20to%20people%20who%20wanted%20unique%20weddings%20as%20a%20mode%20of%20transportation%20for%20brides%20and%20grooms%20and%20for%20other%20occasions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20transformed%20the%20car%20to%20use%20it%20for%20booking%20during%20the%20wedding%20seasons%20so%20that%20our%20family%20will%20be%20able%20to%20earn%20some%20extra%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20Ishwar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20police%20issued%20a%20challan%20of%20Rs%202%2C000%20and%20asked%20to%20remove%20the%20back%20portion%20of%20the%20car.%20I%20have%20invested%20Rs%202.5%20lakh%20in%20this%20car%20and%20worked%20day%20and%20night%20to%20make%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20said%20that%20his%20'rath'%20(chariot)%20was%20intended%20to%20be%20used%20only%20during%20the%20wedding%20season%20and%20will%20not%20ply%20on%20the%20roads%20otherwise.%20He%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20similar%20vehicles%20were%20operating%20in%20other%20regions%20such%20as%20Bihar%20and%20Pratapgarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20of%20his%20creation%20now%20parked%20outside%20a%20police%20station%20in%20Ambedkar%20Nagar%20and%20uploaded%20on%20social%20media%20has%20attracted%20a%20lot%20of%20comments%20from%20users.%20The%20video%20shows%20a%20crowd%20of%20onlookers%20and%20a%20few%20policemen%20standing%20around%20the%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20cited%20safety%20concerns%20as%20the%20primary%20reason%20for%20confiscating%20the%20vehicle.%20The%20police%20said%20the%20car%20was%20modified%20without%20proper%20authorization%20under%20the%20Motor%20Vehicles%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYesterday%2C%20a%20modified%20car%20was%20seized.%20Due%20to%20the%20enforcement%20of%20the%20the%20Model%20code%20of%20Conduct%2C%20police%20have%20been%20conducting%20vehicle%20checks%20and%20this%20modified%20car%20was%20intercepted%20by%20traffic%20police%20during%20one%20such%20inspection.%20Modifications%20require%20permission%20from%20the%20RTO%20department%2C%20and%20the%20vehicle%20was%20seized%20under%20Section%20207%20of%20the%20Motor%20Vehicles%20Act.%20We%20are%20investigating%20further%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Assistant%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20Vishal%20Pandey.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710918360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fc1lagfsk_up-man-modifies-car-into-chopper-cops-seize-it-ani_625x300_20_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-man-modifies-car-into-chopper-cops-seize-vehicle-for-flouting-rules-5274138%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Police%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20ended%20plans%20of%20a%20local%20in%20Ambedkar%20Nagar%20who%20had%20resorted%20to%20the%20quintessential%20Indian%20'jugaad'%20to%20modify%20his%20car%20to%20look%20like%20a%20helicopter.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-man-modifies-car-into-chopper-cops-seize-vehicle-for-flouting-rules-5274138%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fin