it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20we%20celebrated%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fazadi-ka-amrit-mahotsav-today%5C%22%3EAzadi%20Ka%20Amrit%20Mahotsav%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20nearly%2077%20years%20after%20Independence%2C%20India%20seems%20to%20be%20in%20much%20better%20health%20than%20most%20other%20countries%20that%20gained%20independence%20around%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20founding%20fathers%20also%20laid%20a%20solid%20foundation%20for%20an%20election%20apparatus%20necessary%20for%20delivering%20timely%2C%20free%2C%20fair%2C%20and%20credible%20elections%20with%20utmost%20efficiency%20all%20these%20years.%20Part%20XV%20of%20the%20Constitution%20(Articles%20324%20to%20329)%20was%20thoughtfully%20formulated%20and%20enacted%20with%20this%20purpose%2C%20recognising%20elections%20as%20the%20cornerstone%20of%20democratic%20renewal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArticle%20324(1)%20stipulates%20that%20the%20superintendence%2C%20direction%2C%20and%20control%20of%20electoral%20roll%20preparation%20and%20election%20conduct%2C%20including%20those%20for%20Parliament%2C%20state%20assemblies%2C%20and%20offices%20of%20the%20President%20and%20Vice-President%2C%20shall%20be%20vested%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Felection-commission-lok-sabha-polls%5C%22%3EElection%20Commission%20(EC)%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Judicial%20interpretation%20of%20this%20provision%20has%20significantly%20bolstered%20the%20Election%20Commission's%20(EC)%20independence.%20Particularly%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ruling%20in%20the%20matter%20of%20%3Cem%3EM.S.%20Gill%20vs%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%3C%2Fem%3E%20(1977)%20empowered%20the%20EC%20to%20tackle%20multiple%20challenges%20during%20the%20electoral%20process%2C%20ensuring%20timely%20completion%20of%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaking%20Elections%20Cost-Effective%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20authority%20was%20effectively%20utilised%20by%20T.N.%20Seshan%20in%20the%20early%201990s%20to%20further%20elevate%20the%20EC's%20stature.%20In%20the%202016%20Tamil%20Nadu%20assembly%20elections%2C%20the%20poll%20body%20invoked%20the%20ruling%20to%20cancel%20polls%20in%20constituencies%20where%20significant%20cash%20and%20gifts%20were%20distributed%20to%20voters%20during%20campaigning.%20The%20decision%20was%20subsequently%20upheld%20in%20courts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArticle%20324(6)%20mandates%20that%20the%20President%20or%20Governor%2C%20upon%20the%20EC's%20request%2C%20will%20ensure%20required%20staff%20strength%20for%20the%20institution's%20functions.%20This%20provision%20enables%20the%20EC%20to%20mobilise%20a%20temporary%20workforce%20of%20over%2060%20lakh%20polling%20personnel%20and%2090%20lakh%20security%20personnel%20for%20general%20elections%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20managing%20nearly%2096.8%20crore%20voters%20across%2010.5%20lakh%20polling%20stations%20nationwide.%20After%20receiving%20induction%20training%20and%20guidelines%20from%20the%20EC%2C%20these%20personnel%20return%20to%20their%20regular%20duties%20post-election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Expenditure%20Per%20Vote%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20democracies%20lacking%20such%20enabling%20provisions%2C%20a%20permanent%20burden%20of%20large%20manpower%20results%20in%20highly%20expensive%20election%20delivery.%20The%20ECI%20is%20globally%20renowned%20for%20its%20cost-efficient%20delivery%20of%20elections%2C%20compared%20to%20even%20neighbours%20like%20Pakistan%2C%20Bhutan%2C%20and%20Sri%20Lanka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20report%20from%20the%20Centre%20for%20Media%20Studies%20revealed%20that%20during%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20an%20average%20of%20Rs%20700%20was%20spent%20for%20every%20vote.%20This%20amount%20comprised%20Rs%20583%20spent%20by%20candidates%2Fparties%20on%20campaigning%2C%20etc.%2C%20while%20the%20remaining%20Rs%20117%20per%20vote%20constituted%20the%20expenditure%20incurred%20by%20the%20EC%20in%20conducting%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20recent%20report%20in%20newspapers%20highlighted%20that%20the%20EC's%20expenditure%20on%20elections%20grew%20from%20Rs%2010.5%20crore%20(for%2017.5%20crore%20voters)%20in%20the%20general%20elections%20of%201952%20to%20Rs%203%2C870%20crore%20in%20the%202014%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20(for%2083.4%20crore%20voters).%20Comparatively%2C%20many%20developed%20democracies%20allocate%20significantly%20more%20funds%20for%20conducting%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAverage%20Cost%20Continues%20To%20Be%20Low%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20can%20take%20pride%20in%20swiftly%20delivering%20poll%20results%20within%20hours%20once%20the%20vote-counting%20process%20commences%2C%20unlike%20some%20countries%2C%20including%20the%20United%20States%2C%20where%20it%20may%20take%20several%20days%20to%20weeks.%20This%20efficiency%20is%20facilitated%20by%20our%20unique%20voting%20equipment%20-%20the%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machine%20(EVM)%20and%20the%20Voter%20Verifiable%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail%20(VVPAT)%20combined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it's%20noteworthy%20that%20certain%20political%20parties%2C%20which%20remained%20silent%20on%20this%20technology%20when%20they%20secured%20victory%20in%20elections%2C%20raised%20objections%20against%20EVMs%20upon%20facing%20defeat%20in%20other%20polls.%20They%20attributed%20their%20losses%20to%20alleged%20EVM%20tampering%2C%20which%20was%20in%20contrast%20with%20their%20acknowledgement%20of%20the%20technology's%20reliability%20when%20it%20favoured%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20such%20controversies%2C%20the%20EC%20responded%20by%20issuing%20EVM%20challenges%20to%20counter%20the%20allegations.%20Yet%2C%20no%20party%20could%20either%20participate%20in%20these%20challenges%20or%20substantiate%20their%20claims.%20In%20response%20to%20widespread%20concerns%2C%20the%20ECI%20has%20provided%20a%20comprehensive%20document%20on%20their%20website%20titled%20'EVM%20Status%20Paper'%20and%20'EVM%20FAQs'%2C%20addressing%20various%20rumours%20and%20half-truths%20concerning%20EVMs%20in%20detail%2C%20aimed%20at%20informing%20and%20reassuring%20all%20stakeholders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20high%20time%20we%20gave%20the%20commission%20its%20due.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20a%20former%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20of%20India)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710917820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F07q5sg5g_election-commission_640x480_14_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fits-time-indias-election-commission-was-given-its-due-5274193%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ECI%20is%20globally%20renowned%20for%20its%20cost-efficient%20delivery%20of%20elections%2C%20compared%20to%20even%20neighbours%20like%20Pakistan%2C%20Bhutan%2C%20and%20Sri%20Lanka.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fits-time-indias-election-commission-was-given-its-due-5274193%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Centre%20Flags%20Age%20Limit%20After%20Sidhu%20Moose%20Wala's%20Parents%20Have%20Baby%20Via%20IVF%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20flagged%20the%20age%20limit%20for%20conceiving%20a%20child%20via%20the%20IVF%20method%20after%20late%20singer%20Sidhu%20Moose%20Wala's%20parents%20had%20a%20second%20son%20born%20last%20week.%20The%20singer's%20father%2C%20Balkaur%20Singh%2C%20claims%20the%20district%20administration%20has%20been%20harassing%20him%20for%20documents%20about%20the%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20was%20blessed%20with%20a%20child%20last%20Saturday%2C%20nearly%20two%20years%20after%20their%20singer-son%20was%20shot%20dead.%20Charan%20Kaur%2C%2058%2C%20had%20conceived%20the%20child%20th