times-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftim-kildee-brother-of-michigan-rep-dan-killed-by-family-member%2Famp_articleshow%2F108639362.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftim-kildee-brother-of-michigan-rep-dan-killed-by-family-member%2Famp_articleshow%2F108639362.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20CAA%2C%20Civil%20Code%3B%20Chief%20Minister%20To%20Approve%20Governor%3A%20DMK%20Manifesto%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20or%20DMK%20today%20announced%20its%2021%20candidates%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20minister%20MK%20Stalin%20also%20unveiled%20the%20party%20manifesto%20for%20the%20election%20and%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20BJP%20alleging%20that%20the%20party%20had%20destroyed%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20only%20a%20DMK%20manifesto%20but%20the%20people's%20manifesto.%20When%20the%20BJP%20came%20to%20power%20in%202014%2C%20they%20destroyed%20India.%20None%20of%20the%20election%20promises%20were%20fulfilled.%20We%20have%20formed%20the%20INDIA%20Alliance%2C%20and%20we%20will%20form%20our%20government%20in%202024.%20In%20our%20manifesto%2C%20we%20have%20announced%20special%20schemes%20for%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20schemes%20for%20every%20district%20are%20given%20in%20this%20manifesto%26quot%3B%20MK%20Stalin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20DMK%20that%20makes%20the%20manifesto%20before%20elections%20and%20continues%20to%20do%20what%20we%20say%3B%20this%20is%20what%20our%20leaders%20taught%20us.%20As%20Kanimozhi%20said%2C%20we%20went%20all%20over%20the%20state%20and%20listened%20to%20various%20people%26quot%3B%20MK%20Stalin%20added%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20election%20manifesto%20the%20DMK%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20Governor's%20office%20saying%20that%20till%20the%20office%20of%20Governor%20is%20abolished%2C%20a%20Governor%20to%20the%20State%20should%20be%20appointed%20in%20consultation%20with%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20the%20State.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Manifesto%20also%20said%20that%20Article%20361%20which%20provides%20immunity%20from%20criminal%20proceedings%20to%20Governors%20will%20be%20amended.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20DMK%20said%20that%20Thirukural%20will%20be%20made%20as%20'National%20Book'%20while%20National%20Education%20Policy%20and%20NEET%20will%20not%20be%20implemented%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Manifesto%20also%20said%20that%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%20and%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20(UCC)%20will%20not%20be%20implemented%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DMK%20also%20released%20its%20first%20list%20of%2021%20candidates%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20including%2012%20new%20candidates%2C%20with%20Kanimozhi%20contesting%20from%20Thoothukudi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20has%20decided%20to%20field%20Kalanidhi%20Veerasami%20from%20North%20Chennai%2C%20Tamilachi%20Thangapandian%20from%20South%20Chennai%2C%20Dayanidhi%20Maaran%20from%20Central%20Chennai%2C%20TR%20Balu%20from%20Sriperumbatur%2C%20Jagathrachahan%20from%20Arakonam%20and%20Kandhir%20from%20Vellore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnnadurai%20will%20contest%20from%20Thiruvanamalai%2C%20Dharani%20from%20Aarani%2C%20and%20Selvagapathi%20from%20Selam%2C%20Prakash%20from%20Erode%2C%20A%20Raja%20from%20Nilgiris%2C%20Ganapathi%20Rajkumar%20from%20Kovai%2C%20and%20Arun%20Neru%20from%20Perambalur%3B%20Murasoli%20from%20Tanjore%3B%20Thanga%20Tamil%20Selvam%20from%20Theni%3B%20Kanimozhi%20from%20Thuthukudi%3B%20Rani%20from%20Thenkasi%3B%20and%20Malaiarasan%20from%20Kallakurichi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEeswarasamy%20will%20contest%20from%20Pollachi%2C%20Ganapathy%20Rajkumar%20from%20Coimbatore%20and%20Thangathamizchelvan%20from%20Theni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DMK%20is%20fighting%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20Congress%20which%20will%20contest%209%20seats%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20Its%20other%20allies%20are%20VCK%2C%20CPM%2C%20CPI%20which%20will%20contest%20two%20seats%20each.%20IUML%2C%20KMDK%2C%20MDMK%20will%20contest%20on%20one%20seat%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20the%20DMK-led%20alliance%20secured%20a%20landslide%20victory%20by%20bagging%2038%20out%20of%2039%20seats.%20The%20Congress%2C%20which%20was%20also%20a%20part%20of%20the%20alliance%2C%20bagged%208%20seats%20out%20of%20the%20nine%20contested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20AIADMK%20also%20released%20its%20first%20list%20of%2016%20candidates%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20Elections%202024%20on%20Wednesday.%20The%20list%20was%20released%20by%20the%20party%20general%20secretary%2C%20Edappadi%20K%20Palaniswami.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETamil%20Nadu%20is%20voting%20on%20April%2019%20in%20a%20single%20phase%20of%20polling.%20The%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20issued%20a%20notification%20on%20Wednesday%20for%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%202024%20to%20be%20conducted%20on%20April%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20notification%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20informed%20that%20March%2028%20will%20be%20the%20last%20date%20for%20filing%20nominations%20for%20Bihar%20and%20March%2027%20for%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Assam%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Manipur%2C%20Meghalaya%2C%20Mizoram%2C%20Nagaland%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Sikkim%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Tripura%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Andaman%20and%20Nicobar%20Islands%2C%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20Lakshadweep%20and%20Puducherry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolling%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20will%20be%20conducted%20in%20seven%20phases%20across%20the%20nation%20from%20April%2019%20to%20June%201.%20Votes%20will%20be%20counted%20on%20June%204.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20fr