%20kindly%20ask%20for%20understanding%20as%20the%20admission%20will%20be%20conducted%20privately%20to%20ensure%20safety%20and%20prevent%20on-site%20congestion%26quot%3B%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20AllKpop.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fkorean%2Factor-kim-min-kyu-scheduled-to-begin-mandatory-military-service-on-april-1%2Farticleshow%2F108638087.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India's%20Inequality%20at%20Historic%20High%3B%20Wealth%20Concentration%20Shot%20Up%20Sharpest%20Between%202014-5%20and%202022-3%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13093230%2Fkarthik-chandran-uwSbfD1afxI-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Paris-based%20World%20Inequality%20Lab%2C%20with%20pathbreaking%20work%20into%20income%20and%20wealth%20inequality%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwid.world%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FWorldInequalityLab_WP2024_09_Income-and-Wealth-Inequality-in-India-1922-2023_Final.pdf%5C%22%3Ehas%20a%20paper%20out%20on%20the%20state%20of%20inequality%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Titled%2C%20%3Cem%3EIncome%20and%20Wealth%20Inequality%20in%20India%2C%201922-2023%3A%20The%20Rise%20of%20the%20Billionaire%20Raj%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20it%20has%20found%20on%20analysing%20data%20between%201922%20and%202022%20(a%20century%20of%20data%20on%20incomes%20and%20wealth)%2C%20that%20%E2%80%9CBy%202022-23%2C%20top%201%25%20income%20and%20wealth%20shares%20(22.6%25%20and%2040.1%25)%20are%20at%20their%20highest%20historical%20levels%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%20top%201%25%20income%20share%20is%20among%20the%20very%20highest%20in%20the%20world%2C%20higher%20than%20even%20South%20Africa%2C%20Brazil%20and%20US.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20says%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20%E2%80%98billionaire%20raj%E2%80%99%20(a%20term%20used%20to%20define%20the%20post-2010s%20rapid%20rise%20of%20billionaires%20in%20the%20country%2C%20at%20odds%20with%20lives%20of%20millions%2C%20popularised%20by%20James%20Crabtree%E2%80%99s%20book%20of%20the%20same%20name)%20is%20now%20more%20unequal%20than%20the%20British%20colonial%20raj%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20makes%20two%20other%20observations%2C%20one%20on%20income%20tax%20being%20regressive%2C%20if%20seen%20from%20the%20prism%20of%20net%20wealth%20in%20society.%20Also%2C%20the%20poor%20economic%20data%2C%20which%20has%20%E2%80%9Cseen%20a%20decline%20recently.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20finds%20that%20while%20inequality%20has%20been%20rising%20sharply%20in%20India%20since%20the%201980s%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbetween%202014-15%20and%202022-23%2C%20the%C2%A0rise%20of%20top-end%20inequality%20has%20been%20particularly%20pronounced%20in%20terms%20of%20wealth%20concentration.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20listed%20five%20%E2%80%9CKey%20findings%E2%80%9D%20as%20follows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C1.%20Inequality%20declined%20post-independence%20till%20the%20early%201980s%2C%20after%20which%20it%20began%20rising%20and%20has%20skyrocketed%20since%20the%20early%202000s.%20Trends%20of%20top%20income%20and%20wealth%20shares%20track%20each%20other%20over%20the%20entire%20period%20of%20the%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20Between%202014-15%20and%202022-23%2C%20the%20rise%20of%20top-end%20inequality%20has%20been%20particularly%20pronounced%20in%20terms%20of%20wealth%20concentration.%20By%202022-23%2C%20top%201%25%20income%20and%20wealth%20shares%20(22.6%25%20and%2040.1%25)%20are%20at%20their%20highest%20historical%20levels%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%20top%201%25%20income%20share%20is%20among%20the%20very%20highest%20in%20the%20world%2C%20higher%20than%20even%20South%20Africa%2C%20Brazil%20and%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20In%20line%20with%20earlier%20work%2C%20the%20paper%20finds%20suggestive%20evidence%20that%20the%20Indian%20income%20tax%20system%20might%20be%20regressive%20when%20viewed%20from%20the%20lens%20of%20net%20wealth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.%20A%20restructuring%20of%20the%20tax%20code%20to%20account%20for%20both%20income%20and%20wealth%2C%20and%20broad-based%20public%20investments%20in%20health%2C%20education%20and%20nutrition%20are%20needed%20to%20enable%20the%20average%20Indian%2C%20and%20not%20just%20the%20elites%2C%20to%20meaningfully%20benefit%20from%20the%20ongoing%20wave%20of%20globalization.%20Besides%20serving%20as%20a%20tool%20to%20fight%20inequality%2C%20a%20%E2%80%9Csuper%20tax%E2%80%9D%20of%202%25%20on%20the%20net%20wealth%20of%20the%20167%20wealthiest%20families%20in%202022-23%20would%20yield%200.5%25%20of%20national%20income%20in%20revenues%20and%20create%20valuable%20fiscal%20space%20to%20facilitate%20such%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.%20The%20paper%20emphasises%20that%20the%20quality%20of%20economic%20data%20in%20India%20is%20notably%20poor%20and%20has%20seen%20a%20decline%20recently.%20It%20is%20therefore%20likely%20that%20these%20new%20estimates%20represent%20a%20lower%20bound%20to%20actual%20inequality%20levels.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20512px)%2085vw%2C%20512px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F20112906%2FGJDFOJDbsAAYQ6j.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22512%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F20112906%2FGJDFOJDbsAAYQ6j.png%20512w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F20112906%2FGJDFOJDbsAAYQ6j-300x231.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-702452%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22395%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESource%3A%20World%20Inequality%20Lab%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20authors%20are%20Nitin%20Kumar%20Bharti%2C%20Lucas%20Chancel%2C%20Thomas%20Piketty%2C%20and%20Anmol%20Somanchi%20who%20have%20pulled%20together%20%E2%80%9Cnational%20income%20accounts%2C%20wealth%20aggregates%2C%20tax%20tabulations%2C%20rich%20lists%2C%20and%20surveys%20on%20income%2C%20consumption%2C%20and%20wealth%20in%20a%20consistent%20framework%20to%20present%20long%20run%20homogeneous%20series%20of%20income%20and%20wealth%20inequality%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Government%20of%20India%20in%20the%20past%20few%20years%20has%20been%20adept%20at%20refuting%20any%20global%20assessments%20pointing%20to%20economic%20facts%20such%20as%20hunger%20and%20malnutrition%2C%20while%20not%20having%20made%20data%20available%20at%20regular%20intervals%20as%20was%20the%20case%20earlier.%20India%E2%80%99s%20GDP%20data%20itself%20is%20highly%20contested.%20Former%20chief%20economic%20advisor%20Arvind%20Subramanian%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fgdp-numbers-are-mystifying-dont-add-up-former-cea-arvind-subramanian%23%3A~%3Atext%3Deconomy-%2C%2527GDP%2520Numbers%2520Are%2520Mystifying%252C%2520Don%2527t%2520Add%2520Up%2527%2C5%2525%252C%2527%2520he%2520said.%5C%22%3Ehas%20expressed%20surprise%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20how%20the%20GDP%20has%20been%20said%20to%20be%20rising.%20India%20has%20missed%20its%20date%20for%20the%20decadal%20census%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20140%20years%2C%20in%202021%2C%20citing%20COVID-19.%20India%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fwho-is-disputing-indias-covid-death-numbers-so-govt-wants-to-bury-global-report%5C%22%3Ehas%20issues%20with%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20WHO%20data%20on%20underestimation%20of%20the%20Covid%20death%20toll%20by%20ten%20times.%20It%20is%20the%20only%20country%20in%20the%20world%20which%20contests%20WHO%E2%80%99s%20Covid%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710915070000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13093230%2Fkarthik-chandran-uwSbfD1afxI-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Findias-inequality-at-historic-high-wealth-concentration-shot-up-sharpest-between-2014-5-and-2022-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Data%20on%20India%20for%20a%20century%20has%20revealed%20income%20and%20wealth%20inequality%20now%20as%20being%20worse%20than%20during%20British%20colonial%20rule%2C%20according%20to%20the%20World%20Inequality%20Lab.%20Using%20%E2%80%9Cbillionaire%20raj%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20present%20times%2C%20research%20has%20found%20that%20inequality%20declined%20post-independence%20till%20the%201980s%2C%20rose%20afterwards%20and%20is%20%E2%80%9Cskyrocketing%20now%E2%80%9D.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Findias-inequality-at-historic-high-wealth-concentration-shot-up-sharpest-between-2014-5-and-2022-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kerala%3A%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Lone%20Muslim%20Candidate%20%E2%80%98Sidelined%E2%80%99%20at%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Roadshow%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F20111215%2FGJBaWRLWQAAmam1.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20or%20CPI(M)%20accused%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20of%20sidelining%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%E2%80%99s%20(BJP)%20lone%20Muslim%20candidate%20in%20Kerala%20during%20a%20roadshow%20in%20the%20state%20on%20Tuesday%20(March%2019).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20conducted%20a%20roadshow%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EPalakkad%20with%20candidates%20from%20Palakkad%20and%20the%20adjacent%20Ponnani%20constituency%20(Malappuram%20district).%20However%2C%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Malappuram%20candidate%20Abdul%20Salam%20was%20not%20invited%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20event%2C%20PTI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Felections%2Findia%2Frow-over-sidelining-bjps-lone-muslim-candi