ain%20or%20benefit%20and%20quid%20pro%20quo%20in%20the%20discharge%20of%20public%20duties.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lokpal%20noted%20that%2C%20as%20per%20CBI%20report%20presented%20to%20them%2C%20the%20allegation%20that%20Moitra%20shared%20her%20login%20credentials%20and%20password%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Member%20Portal%20with%20the%20Dubai-based%20businessman%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%20was%20%3Cem%3Eprima%20facie%20substantiate%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20Inquiry%2C%20it%20was%20revealed%20that%20Shri%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%20had%20sworn%20an%20affidavit%20stating%20that%20the%20RPS%20had%20shared%20her%20Member%20Portal%20Password%20with%20him%20in%20order%20to%20enable%20him%20to%20post%20questions.%20He%20also%20confirmed%20upon%20inquiry%20that%20all%20the%2058%20(fifty-eight)%20online%20questions%2C%20which%20the%20RPS%20had%20asked%2C%20were%20typed%20by%20him.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lokpal%20order%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20mention%20either%20Moitra%20or%20the%20complainant%E2%80%99s%20name%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Flokpal-orders-cbi-probe-into-charges-against-mahua-moitra%2Farticle67969897.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20is%20already%20looking%20into%20the%20matter%2C%20as%20was%20suggest%20by%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Ethics%20Committee%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fmahua-moitra-cbi-fir-lok-sabha-ethics-committee-report-cash-for-query-case-2487362-2024-01-11%5C%22%3Ehad%20asked%20for%20the%20ethics%20committee%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20January.%20As%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fat-least-three-critical-flaws-in-the-ethics-committee-report-on-mahua-moitra%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20ethics%20committee%20report%20was%20severely%20flawed%20and%20raised%20several%20questions.%20The%20c