companies%2Fnews%2Fall-riders-wear-red-zomato-drops-green-colour-from-pure-veg-fleet-124032000140_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fall-riders-wear-red-zomato-drops-green-colour-from-pure-veg-fleet-124032000140_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Zomato%20Announces%20'Pure%20Veg'%20Delivery%20Fleet%2C%20Revokes%20Colour%20Segregation%20After%20Blowback%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F20085940%2FGJBvWRracAAVEIl.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EFood%20delivery%20company%20Zomato%20has%20come%20under%20criticism%20for%20its%20decision%20to%20introduce%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpure%20veg%20fleet%E2%80%9D%20of%20delivery%20vehicles%2C%20which%20will%20not%20deliver%20food%20from%20any%20restaurants%20that%20serve%20egg%2C%20fish%2C%20chicken%20or%20any%20sort%20of%20meat.%20Originally%2C%20company%20CEO%20Deepinder%20Goyal%20announced%20that%20this%20fleet%20would%20wear%20green%20and%20have%20green%20delivery%20boxes%20on%20their%20motorcycle%20so%20that%20they%20could%20be%20told%20apart%2C%20but%20later%20said%20in%20an%20%E2%80%9Cupdate%E2%80%9D%20that%20the%20company%20decided%20not%20to%20have%20this%20segregation%20and%20all%20delivery%20executives%20would%20continue%20to%20wear%20red.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20%E2%80%9Cupdate%E2%80%9D%20came%20after%20many%20people%20on%20social%20media%20pointed%20out%20how%20this%20colour%20segregation%20could%20be%20used%20to%20target%20those%20eating%20non-vegetarian%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20%5Ball%20delivery%20executives%20wearing%20red%5D%20will%20ensure%20that%20our%20red%20uniform%20delivery%20partners%20are%20not%20incorrectly%20associated%20with%20non-veg%20food%2C%20and%20blocked%20by%20any%20RWAs%20or%20societies%20during%20any%20special%20days%E2%80%A6%20our%20rider%E2%80%99s%20physical%20safety%20is%20of%20paramount%20importance%20to%20us.%20We%20now%20realise%20that%20even%20some%20of%20our%20customers%20could%20get%20into%20trouble%20with%20their%20landlords%2C%20and%20that%20would%20not%20be%20a%20nice%20if%20that%20happened%20because%20of%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20Goyal%20said%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoyal%20claimed%20that%20a%20separate%20fleet%20was%20needed%20because%20the%20%E2%80%9Csmell%E2%80%9D%20of%20non-vegetarian%20food%20may%20bother%20people.%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6why%20did%20we%20need%20to%20separate%20the%20fleets%3F%20Because%20despite%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20best%20efforts%2C%20sometimes%20the%20food%20spills%20into%20the%20delivery%20boxes.%20In%20those%20cases%2C%20the%20smell%20of%20the%20previous%20order%20travels%20to%20the%20next%20order%2C%20and%20may%20lead%20to%20the%20next%20order%20smelling%20of%20the%20previous%20order.%20For%20this%20reason%2C%20we%20had%20to%20separate%20the%20fleet%20for%20veg%20orders%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoyal%2C%20however%2C%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20the%20most%20stringent%20criticism%20of%20this%20move%20%E2%80%93%20that%20segregation%20of%20this%20kind%2C%20in%20a%20county%20like%20India%2C%20can%20be%20communal%20and%20casteist%20by%20its%20very%20nature.%20%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20most%20important%20aspects%20of%20caste%20is%20food%20pollution%2C%E2%80%9D%20A.F.%20Mathew%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20IIM%20Kozhikode%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fto-solve-for-dietary-preference-of-100-vegetarians-zomato-introduces-a-pure-veg-fleet%2Farticle67969197.ece%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20will%20have%20to%20extend%20to%20whoever%20will%20deliver%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20continued.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20if%20there%20is%20a%20Muslim%20driver%20bringing%20in%20a%20customer%E2%80%99s%20vegetarian%20food%3F%20%E2%80%A6%20Where%20is%20this%20going%3F%20Will%20Jains%20deliver%20for%20Jains%2C%20and%20Brahmins%20for%20Brahmins%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffood%2Findia-food-eating-vegetarianism%5C%22%3E2018%20article%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20scholars%20Balmurli%20Natrajan%20and%20Suraj%20Jacob%20pointed%20out%20that%20%E2%80%9CThe%20extent%20of%20overall%20vegetarianism%20is%20much%20less%20than%20common%20claims%20and%20stereotypes%20suggest%3B%20survey%20estimates%20show%20that%20between%2023%25%20and%2037%25%20of%20the%20population%20of%20India%20is%20vegetarian.%20Thus%2C%20far%20from%20being%20a%20vegetarian%20nation%2C%20India%20is%20a%20meat-eating%20majority%20nation.%20The%20notion%20of%20%E2%80%98non-vegetarian%E2%80%99%20and%20the%20discourse%20around%20vegetarianism%2C%20then%2C%20reflect%20the%20hegemony%20enjoyed%20(thus%20far)%20by%20the%20%E2%80%98minority%E2%80%99%20vegetarian%20population.%E2%80%9D%20Even%20most%20of%20the%20majority%20Hindu%20community%2C%20the%20authors%20stated%20based%20on%20government%20data%2C%20eat%20non-vegetarian%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20leaders%20from%20opposition%20parties%20and%20trade%20unions%20also%20criticised%20Zomato%E2%80%99s%20announcement.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20last%20time%20someone%20on%20Zomato%20requested%20for%20a%20delivery%20partner%20of%20a%20particular%20religion%2C%20Goyal%20said%20%E2%80%98food%20has%20no%20religion%E2%80%99.%20Today%2C%20he%20seems%20to%20have%20gone%20back%20on%20this.%20I%20ask%20him%20directly%2C%20is%20he%20now%20going%20to%20categorise%20delivery%20partners%20on%20the%20lines%20of%20caste%2C%20community%20and%20religion%3F%E2%80%9D%20Sheikh%20Salauddin%2C%20president%20of%20the%20Indian%20Federation%20of%20App-Based%20Transport%20Workers%20union%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710905432000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F20085940%2FGJBvWRracAAVEIl.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fzomato-announces-pure-veg-delivery-fleet-re