th%20all%20student%20organisations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%5BA%20forum%20of%5D%20All%2016%20opposition%20parties%20%5Bthe%20United%20Opposition%20Forum%20of%20Assam%5D%20%E2%80%93%20of%20which%20I%20am%20the%20chairman%20%E2%80%93%20%5Bis%5D%20ready%20to%20fight%20against%20the%20CAA.%20But%20as%20elections%20are%20coming%2C%20we%20are%20appealing%20to%20the%20people%20that%20if%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20the%20CAA%2C%20then%20vote%20against%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESarbanand%20Sonowal%20%5Bfielded%20by%20the%20BJP%20in%20Dibrugarh%20this%20time%5D%20will%20lose%20because%20he%20was%20CM%20when%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fassam-anti-citizenship-amendment-act-protest-deaths%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efive%20people%20were%20killed%20during%20CAA%20protests%20in%202019%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESarma%20has%20also%20said%20that%20Assam%20has%20already%20taken%20a%20lot%20of%20burden%20till%201971%20%5Band%5D%20we%20cannot%20take%20anymore.%20That%20was%20a%20formal%20statement%20given%3B%20now%20only%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20power%2C%20he%20is%20doing%20this%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Assam.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20I%20am%20appealing%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Assam%20that%20if%20you%20are%20against%20the%20CAA%2C%20then%20you%20should%20vote%20for%20the%20INDIA%20alliance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710858621000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F30182721%2FF1TiOWFaAAAxnsC-1.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fhimanta-using-two-policies-of-purchasing-and-threatening-assam-congress-chief-bhupen-borah%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Borah%20also%20said%20that%20with%20the%20BJP%20government%20notifying%20the%20rules%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20Assam%2