ure%20that%20whatever%20we%20produce%20will%20be%20manufactured%20by%20us%20in%20order%20to%20utilise%20the%20massive%20talent%20in%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBeing%20an%20automotive%20guy%2C%20we%20were%20very%20sure%20that%20this%20is%20the%20industry%20we%20wanted%20to%20enter.%20But%20this%20centuries-old%20industry%20is%20a%20tough%20one%20to%20enter.%20However%2C%20there%20is%20a%20huge%20change%20in%20the%20industry%20as%20people%20are%20accepting%20EVs%20more%20now.%20We%20wanted%20to%20create%20a%20niche%20around%20lifestyle%20mobility%20and%20this%20was%20our%20window%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Arvind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20that%20Arvind%20and%20Vipin%20were%20sure%20about%20was%20that%20they%20wanted%20to%20have%20a%20focus%20area%20and%20a%20problem%20they%20wanted%20to%20solve.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLiving%20in%20a%20small%20town%2C%20what%20we%20understood%20was%20that%20India%20is%20not%20producing%20enough%20blue%20and%20white%20collared%20jobs%20for%20the%20educated%20youth.%20Another%20thing%20that%20we%20noticed%20is%20that%20because%20of%20the%20lack%20of%20jobs%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20youth%20in%20small%20towns%20become%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F291959%2Fbest-products-from-northeast-india-sustainable-startup-entrepreneurs-small-businesses%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esmall%20entrepreneurs%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20of%20them%20need%20mobility%20and%20they%20prefer%20two-wheelers%20as%20they%20are%20cheaper%20and%20faster.%20We%20realised%20how%20these%20small%20entrepreneurs%20need%20a%20two-wheeler%20that%20is%20efficient%2C%20electric%20but%20most%20importantly%20has%20ample%20amount%20of%20space%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20became%20the%20primary%20focal%20point%20when%20the%20duo%20started%20to%20design%20their%20EV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EStylish%2C%20sustainable%20and%20green%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20why%20he%20named%20his%20company%20River%2C%20Arvind%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CJust%20like%20a%20river%20which%20is%20giving%20and%20helps%20others%20thrive%2C%20we%20as%20a%20business%20want%20to%20help%20other%20small%20businesses%20thrive%20with%20the%20right%20transportation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20utility%2C%20what%20they%20wanted%20to%20focus%20on%20as%20a%20company%20was%20the%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FEV-5-1710756910.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vipin%20George%20and%20Arvind%20Mani%2C%20founders%20of%20River.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FEV-5-1710756910.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FEV-5-1710756910-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FEV-5-1710756910-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FEV-5-1710756910-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FEV-5-1710756910-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345055%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVipin%20George%20and%20Arvind%20Mani%2C%20founders%20of%20River.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20India%2C%20we%20noticed%20that%20if%20something%20is%20high%20in%20utility%2C%20then%20its%20design%20is%20neglected.%20However%2C%20since%20we%20want%20to%20appeal%20to%20the%20youth%2C%20we%20want%20to%20give%20them%20the%20best%20design%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20youth%20knows%20what%20they%20want%20from%20the%20vehicle%20but%20also%20they%20want%20it%20to%20have%20some%20personality.%20So%20this%20became%20our%20driving%20force%2C%20we%20combine%20utility%20with%20design%20to%20create%20a%20product%20that%20is%20eco-friendly%20and%20suits%20our%20users.%20Just%20as%20a%20farmer%20drives%20his%20truck%20or%20tractor%20with%20pride%2C%20we%20want%20a%20small%20entrepreneur%2C%20say%20a%20carpenter%2C%20to%20have%20pride%20in%20driving%20his%20business%20vehicle%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scooter%20has%20the%20largest%20storage%20capacity%20of%2055%20litre%20which%20is%20three%20times%20more%20than%20the%20average%20scooter%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20have%20the%20largest%20floor%20board%20since%20people%20utilise%20every%20inch%20of%20the%20vehicle%20in%20India.%20You%20will%20often%20see%20grocery%20bags%2C%20school%20bags%2C%20and%20even%20kids%20standing%20on%20them.%20So%20in%20our%20product%2C%20we%20have%20included%20%E2%80%98Lock%20and%20Load%20Pannier%20Mounts%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20are%20sturdy%20alloy%20mounts%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20scooter.%20Attach%20pannier%20boxes%2C%20load%20up%20and%20make%20the%20most%20of%20the%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20love%20the%20hustle%20culture%20of%20our%20youth%20and%20we%20have%20made%20a%20vehicle%20designed%20especially%20for%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vehicle%20also%20has%20a%2012-litre%20lockable%20glove%20box%20with%20a%20USB%20charger.%20%E2%80%9CStore%20and%20lock%20up%20your%20valuables%20for%20safety%2C%20and%20easily%20access%20them%20while%20being%20seated%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20range%20anxiety%20that%20most%20people%20deal%20with%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20scooters%20are%20usually%20used%20by%20Indians%20to%20drive%20within%20the%20cities%20and%20inter-city%20usage%20is%20usually%20via%20a%20motorcycle.%20Designed%20specifically%20for%20inter-city%20travel%2C%20we%20have%20offered%20a%20range%20of%20103%20km%20when%20fully-charged.%20So%20this%20way%2C%20a%20customer%20will%20be%20charging%20the%20vehicle%20once%20every%20three%20to%20four%20days.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC3P2LIUrMz5%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC3P2LIUrMz5%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC3P2LIUrMz5%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20River%20Mobility%20(%40rideriver.in)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F300789%2Fretrofitting-how-to-convert-your-old-cars-into-electric-vehicles%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20EV%20is%20currently%20available%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20three%20colours%20%E2%80%94%20Monsoon%20Blue%2C%20Summer%20Red%20and%20Spring%