harging%2C%20here%20is%20all%20you%20need%20to%20about%20the%20'SUV%20of%20EV%20Scooters'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345050%2Fev-scooter-in-india-storage-options-arvind-mani-vipin-george-startup-river-in-bengaluru%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'EVMs%20Are%20The%20Secret%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Success'%3A%20Chorus%20For%20Change%20In%20A%20Remote%20Pocket%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F19174248%2FScreen-Shot-2024-03-19-at-5.37.43-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChordiha%20(Uttar%20Pradesh)%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20India%20will%20come%20to%20know%20about%20the%20victors%20and%20the%20vanquished%20in%20the%20general%20elections%20on%20June%204%2C%202024.%20However%2C%20the%20residents%20of%20Chordiha%2C%20the%20largest%20village%20of%20the%20Dalits%20under%20the%20Salempur%20parliamentary%20constituency%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20have%20uncovered%20the%20%E2%80%9Csecret%E2%80%9D%20behind%20the%20strength%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%20They%20are%20deciphering%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmechanism%E2%80%9D%20to%20counter%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machines%20(EVMs)%20are%20the%20secret%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20%5BPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%5D%20success.%20If%20we%20are%20given%20ballot%20papers%20to%20cast%20our%20votes%2C%20the%20game%20will%20change%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shriramniwas%20Prasad%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Chordiha%20village.%20He%20was%20playing%20cards%20along%20with%20his%20fellow%20villagers%20near%20an%20under%20construction%20house%20at%20the%20eastern%20edge%20of%20the%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20how%20do%20they%20know%20that%20the%20EVMs%20are%20manipulated%2C%20Manoj%20Ram%20said%2C%C2%A0%E2%80%9CVisit%20our%20booths%20on%20the%20polling%20day.%20You%20won%E2%80%99t%20find%20any%20of%20us%20voting%20for%20the%20BJP.%20But%20it%20will%20be%20a%20totally%20opposite%20result.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20further%20underline%20that%20complaining%20to%20the%20electoral%20officials%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20of%20much%20help.%C2%A0%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ESab%20uskaa%20aadmi%20hai%20%3C%2Fem%3E(all%20are%20BJP%20men)%3Cem%3E%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sitaram%2C%20without%20mincing%20words%20in%20between%20inspecting%20his%20playing%20cards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20Ramashray%20Prasad%20suggested%20a%20way%20out%2C%20%E2%80%9CCast%20your%20votes%20by%2012%20noon.%20There%20will%20be%20less%20chances%20of%20manipulation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20yes!!!%20We%20will%20do%20that%20this%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20others%20said%20in%20a%20chorus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESitaram%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9COver%20with%20casting%20our%20votes%20by%2012%20noon%20we%20should%20ask%20the%20presiding%20officers%20to%20seal%20the%20EVMs%20and%20go%2C%20depositing%20it%20at%20the%20strong%20room.%20Why%20should%20they%20stay%20till%20the%20late%20evening%20when%20all%20the%20votes%20are%20cast%3F%20They%20might%20use%20the%20time%20to%20manipulate%20the%20EMVs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20villagers%20vowed%20to%20not%20leave%20the%20polling%20booths%20till%20the%20EVMs%20are%20%E2%80%9Csealed%20and%20packed%20off%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20two%E2%80%93kilometer%20single-lane%20stretch%20branching%20out%20from%20the%20main%20Mehrauna-Gorakhpur%20highway%20at%20Kundaulia%20under%20the%20Deoria%20district%20of%20Eastern%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20takes%20one%20to%20Chordiha%2C%20inhabited%20largely%20by%20the%20Harijans%20%E2%80%94%20equivalent%20of%20what%20is%20known%20as%20the%20Jatavs%20of%20Western%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20to%20which%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%20president%20Mayawati%20belongs%20%E2%80%94%20apart%20from%20the%20Dusadhs%2C%20Dhobis%20and%20other%20sub-castes%20of%20the%20Dalit%20community.%20It%20is%20said%20to%20be%20the%20largest%20village%20in%20the%20district%20and%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpowerhouse%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20Dalit%20politics%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReasons%20for%20anger%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chordiha%20residents%20appeared%20to%20be%20angrier%20with%20Modi%20than%20the%20BJP%20at%20large%20and%20had%20their%20own%20logic%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20why%20they%20were%20angry%20with%20the%20prime%20minister%20even%20when%20he%20got%20the%20Ram%20temple%20built%20at%20Ayodhya%20and%20everyone%20in%20the%20village%20might%20be%20getting%20five%20kilograms%20of%20food-grains%20and%20money%20under%20various%20welfare%20schemes%20initiated%20by%20the%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0They%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20the%20problem%20of%20you%20people.%20You%20come%20from%20faraway%20lands%20during%20the%20poll%20time%20and%20start%20asking%20%3Cem%3Ejhooth-mooth%20ka%20sawal%3C%2Fem%3E%20(unreal%20questions).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20youth%20from%20our%20community%20from%20the%20neighbouring%20Patna%20village%20was%20a%20good%20folk-singer.%20He%20uploaded%20a%20song%20on%20YouTube.%20The%20policemen%20arrested%20him%20and%20put%20him%20in%20jail.%20Now%2C%20we%20get%20the%20policemen%20visiting%20us%20invariably%20and%20looking%20or%20those%20who%20sing%20folk%20songs%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20told%20that%20the%20police%20are%20under%20the%20state%20government%20headed%20by%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%2C%20Kishun%20replied%2C%20%E2%80%9CBut%20Yogi%20is%20under%20Modi.%20Once%20Modi%20is%20finished%20Yogi%20will%20be%20gone.%20And%20it%E2%80%99s%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%E2%80%A6%20It%E2%80%99s%20time%20to%20think%20of%20Modi%2C%20not%20others.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20present%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%2062%20Lok%20Sabha%20MPs%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20while%20its%20alliance%20partner%20Apna%20Dal%20has%20two%20MPs%20from%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20villagers%20were%20aware%20of%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20controversy%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20verdict%20about%20it.%20Shriramniwas%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20%3Cem%3EChud%20saheb%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5BD.Y.%20Chadrachud%5D%20is%20an%20honest%20and%20fair%20judge.%20He%20has%20exposed%20the%20farce.%20But%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20the%20end%20of%20the%20problem.%20The%20eventual%20solution%20lies%20in%20removal%20of%20Modi%20from%20power.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20(PM)%20has%20captured%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20with%20his%20own%20men.%20He%20removed%20Raghuram%C2%A0%3Cem%3Esaheb%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E(Raghuram%20Rajan)%20and%20deployed%20his%20own%20men%20in%20the%20banks%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESitaram%20underlined%20that%20they%20know%20about%20all%20these%20developments%20at%20the%20national%20level%20since%20they%20have%20%E2%80%9Cmobile%20phones%E2%80%9D.%20He%20added%20that%20they%20%E2%80%9Cwatch%20and%20listen%20to%20the%20news%20on%20YouTube%20and%20Facebook%E2%80%9D.%20Further%2C%20Sitaram%20pointed%20out%20that%20they%20discuss%20political%20issues%20among%20themselves%20and%20many%20youths%20in%20the%20villages%20%E2%80%9Cwho%20are%20educated%20but%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20jobs%E2%80%9D%20explain%20the%20matters%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20not%20the%20BJP%2C%20whom%20will%20they%20vote%20for%3F%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20vote%20for%C2%A0%3Cem%3EBehanji%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5BMayawati%E2%80%99s%20BSP%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20villagers%20mentioned.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20informed%20that%20Mayawati%20is%20said%20to%20be%20%E2%80%98clandestinely%E2%80%99%20supporting%20the%20BJP%20under%20the%20pressure%20from%20the%20central%20bureau%20of%20investigation%20and%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%2C%20Ramashray%20Prasad%20argued%C2%A0%20with%20an%20air%20of%20finality%2C%20%E2%80%9CThese%20are%20all%20lies%20circulated%20by%20the%20BJP%20supporters.%20%3Cem%3EBehanji%3C%2Fem%3E%20will%20never%20support%20the%20BJP.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20villagers%20also%20believe%20that%20Mayawati%20will%20join%20hands%20with%20the%20Congress-Samajwadi%20Party%20alliance%20which%20currently%20looks%20like%20offering%20the%20main%20challenge%20to%20the%20BJP.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20don%E2%80%99t%20know!!%20There%20is%20still%20time%20left.%C2%A0%3Cem%3EAntatogatwa%20alliance%20hoga%3C%2Fem%3E%20(eventually%20there%20will%20be%20an%20alliance)%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shriramniwas%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20only%20source%20of%20anxiety%20are%20EVMs.%20Nothing%20else%20can%20stop%20from%20driving%20Modi%20out%20of%20power.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffor-all-the-bluster-why-bjp-needs-a-maha-alliance-in-uttar-pradesh%5C%22%3E%20For%20All%20the%20Bluster%2C%20Why%20BJP%20Needs%20a%20Maha-Alliance%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EOut%20of%20the%2080%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituencies%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%2017%20are%20reserved%20for%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes.%20The%20state%20will%20vote%20in%20all%20the%20seven%20phases%20%E2%80%94%20April%2019%2C%20April%2026%2C%20May%207%2C%20May%2013%2C%20May%2020%2C%20May%2025%20and%20June%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chordiha%20residents%20firmly%20believe%20that%20the%20BJP%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20able%20to%20win%20over%20400%20seats%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20unlike%20the%20claim%20of%20%E2%80%98400-%3Cem%3Epaar%20%3C%2Fem%3E(over%20400%20seats)%E2%80%99%20made%20by%20Modi%20and%20the%20other%20BJP%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJust%20move%20out%20to%20other%20villages%20two%20kilometers%20away%20from%20the%20Kundauli%20and%20Laar%20bazaar%20on%20the%20north%20and%20south%20of%20the%20Mehrauna-Gorakhpur%20highway%2C%20you%20will%20understand%E2%80%A6.%E2%80%9D%20argued%20Ramashray%2C%20showing%20a%20cluster%20of%20seven%20houses%20all%20belonging%20to%20the%20Brahmin%20families%20on%20the%20western%20outskirts%20of%20the%20village%20with%20his%20index%20finger%20and%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9COnly%20the%20members%20at%20those%20seven%20homes%20will%20vote%20for%20Modi%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20their%20anger%20against%20the%20BJP%20and%20also%20their%20collective%20will%20to%20drive%20the%20Hindutva%20party%20out%20of%20power%2C%20what%20the%20Chordiha%20residents%20might%20not%20understand%20is%20that%20Mayawati%20might%20go%20her%20separate%20way%20and%20they%20in%20no%20way%20represent%20the%20microcosm%20of%20a%20society%20as%20diverse%20and%20vast%20as%20the%20state%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20And%20their%20sentiment%20might%20not%20translate%20into%20what%20they%20wish%20in%20their%20own%20world%20confined%20within%20the%20periphery%20of%20the%20nondescript%20Chordiha%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENalin%20Verma%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%2C%20author%2C%20media%20educator%20and%20independent%20researcher%20in%20folklore.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710856818000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F19174248%2FScreen-Shot-2024-03-19-at-5.37.43-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fchorus-for-change-and-anger-against-prime-minister-modi-in-a-remote-pocket-of-uttar-pradesh%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Chordiha%20residents%20firmly%20believe%20that%20the%20BJP%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20win%20over%20400%20seats%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20unlike%20the%20claim%20of%20%E2%80%98400-paar%20(over%20400%20seats)%E2%80%99%20made%20by%20Modi%20and%20the%20other%20BJP%20leaders.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A53%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fchorus-for-change-and-anger-against-prime-minis