d%20The%20Right%20Lawyers%3B%20Earns%20Rs%201.25%20Crore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20Shreya%20Sharma%2C%20a%2025-year-old%20lawyer%20from%20Pune%2C%20met%20a%20woman%20in%20her%20fifties%20who%20was%20facing%20a%20property%20dispute%2C%20she%20realised%20that%20there%20was%20no%20one%20to%20advise%20her.%20The%20woman%20was%20clueless%20about%20which%20lawyer%20to%20approach%2C%20what%20the%20procedure%20would%20entail%2C%20and%20this%20only%20added%20to%20her%20worries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20many%20Indians%20who%20face%20similar%20legal%20conundrums%2C%20as%20legal%20literacy%20remains%20poor.%20Recognising%20this%20gap%2C%20and%20to%20enable%20access%20to%20the%20right%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329588%2Fentrepreneur-startup-green-energy-foundation-gud-mom-millet-products-help-organic-farmers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elegal%20information%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Shreya%20started%20%E2%80%98Rest%20The%20Case%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20legal%20aggregator%20platform%20in%20Pune.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20found%20her%20calling%20when%20she%20was%20working%20on%20a%20project%20which%20involved%20interviewing%20lawyers%20as%20a%20student%20at%20Cardiff%20University.%20She%20searched%20for%20legal%20information%20online%2C%20and%20found%20many%20credible%20websites%20offering%20this%2C%20along%20with%20a%20list%20of%20lawyers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20was%20something%20like%20this%20available%20in%20India%3F%20The%2025-year-old%20found%20that%20there%20wasn%E2%80%99t.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERest%20The%20Case%20provides%20legal%20information%2C%20from%20basic%20templates%20to%20bare%20acts%2C%20legal%20drafting%2C%20and%20a%20list%20of%20lawyers.%20It%20has%20also%20created%20a%20network%20base%20for%20lawyers%20of%20different%20specialisations%20to%20connect%20with%20clients.%20More%20than%201%2C200%20lawyers%20from%20across%20the%20country%20are%20already%20a%20