0the%2032-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20she%20took%20a%20break%20from%20work%20to%20understand%20the%20nitty-gritties%20of%20farming%20as%20she%20did%20not%20have%20any%20agricultural%20background.%20To%20begin%20with%2C%20Keya%20started%20growing%20about%2030%20varieties%20of%20microgreens%20in%20a%20vertical%20set-up%20made%20on%20the%20terrace.%20Soon%2C%20she%20started%20supplying%20them%20to%20restaurants%2C%20and%20within%20six%20months%2C%20she%20on-boarded%2050%20clients.%20This%20boosted%20her%20confidence%20and%20allowed%20her%20to%20establish%20retail%20connections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20this%20transition%2C%20I%20started%20researching%20on%20the%20kinds%20of%20crops%20grown%20in%20other%20countries%20that%20had%20gained%20a%20lot%20of%20traction%20in%20agriculture.%20Compared%20to%20countries%20in%20South%20and%20Central%20America%2C%20India%20has%20not%20graduated%20beyond%20growing%20major%20basic%20crops%20like%20paddy%2C%20sugarcane%2C%20and%20wheat%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-1-1-1710699243.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%202021%2C%20Keya%20set%20up%20Farm2Fam%20to%20cultivate%20exotic%20berries.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-1-1-1710699243.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-1-1-1710699243-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-1-1-1710699243-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-1-1-1710699243-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-1-1-1710699243-150x7