egree%20in%20political%20science.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20shares%20that%20she%20also%20attends%20handicraft%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344526%2Fsamvaad-tata-steel-foundation-celebrates-culture-of-tribes-of-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eart%20workshops%20by%20Samvaa%3C%2Fa%3Ed%20to%20learn%20about%20new%20market%20trends%20and%20skills%20that%20can%20help%20her%20with%20more%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20set%20up%20a%20stall%20in%20an%20exhibition%2C%20there%20is%20so%20much%20more%20than%20just%20selling%20the%20paintings.%20I%20learnt%20that%20if%20you%20wear%20traditional%20clothing%20in%20exhibitions%2C%20more%20people%20tend%20to%20visit%20your%20stall.%20The%20way%20you%20place%20your%20paintings%20in%20a%20small%20area%20also%20matters%20a%20lot.%20For%20example%2C%20always%20have%20a%20subtle%20and%20muted%20painting%20between%20two%20colourful%20paintings.%20It%20serves%20as%20a%20palette%20cleanser.%20Even%20the%20way%20you%20talk%20to%20people%20and%20tell%20your%20story%20matters.%20I%20learnt%20all%20this%20and%20more%20from%20experts%20who%20conduct%20Samvaad%20workshops%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sumanti%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FUntitled-design-1-1710338733.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sumanti%20Devi%20(L)%20Oraon%20painting%20in%20process.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FUntitled-design-1-1710338733.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FUntitled-design-1-1710338733-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FUntitled-design-1-1710338733-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2