dy%20(under%20the%20latest%20%E2%80%98PM-Surya%20Ghar%3A%20Muft%20Bijli%20Yojana%E2%80%99).%20The%20consumer%20ends%20up%20paying%20only%20about%20Rs%201.2%20lakh%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FjClnfkmeWKY%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22New%20Subsidy%20Alert%20Feb%202024%20l%20Prime%20Minister%20Surya%20Ghar%20Muft%20Bijli%20Yojana%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22281%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20this%203-kW%20system%2C%20consumers%20end%20up%20saving%20Rs%203%2C000%20to%20Rs%203%2C500%20a%20month%20in%20electricity%20bills.%20In%20a%20year%2C%20this%20amounts%20to%20approximately%20Rs%2036%2C000%20to%20Rs%2040%2C000%20a%20year%20in%20electricity%20savings.%20In%20about%20three%20to%20four%20years%2C%20you%20can%20recover%20all%20your%20initial%20investment.%20Following%20this%2C%20this%20solar%20installation%20can%20give%20you%20free%20electricity%20for%20the%20next%2020%20to%2025%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20consumer%20on%20a%20five-year%20EMI%2C%20their%20net%20investment%20comes%20down%20to%20zero%20because%20their%20down%20payment%20gets%20covered%20by%20the%20subsidy%20given%20by%20the%20Union%20Government%2C%20and%20monthly%20EMIs%20are%20covered%20through%20monthly%20electricity%20savings%20achieved%20after%20going%20solar.%20In%20net%20terms%2C%20the%20family%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20to%20arrange%20any%20substantial%20sums.%20We%20call%20this%20the%20zero%20investment%20scheme%20of%20solar%2C%20which%20we%20educate%20the%20consumer%20about%20during%20a%20consultation%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Neeraj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-em